a:10:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:57:"Để làm lập trình viên sau 1 năm, nên học gì?";s:4:"link";s:66:"http://techtalk.vn/de-lam-lap-trinh-vien-sau-1-nam-nen-hoc-gi.html";s:11:"description";s:597:"<div>Th&#7921;c s&#7921; th&igrave; m&igrave;nh ch&#7881; m&#7899;i &#273;i l&agrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7847;n 1 n&#259;m, skill c&#361;ng ch&#432;a c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u n&ecirc;n c&#361;ng kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; ch&eacute;m gi&oacute; s&acirc;u v&agrave;o k&#7929; thu&#7853;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c. L&uacute;c tr&#432;&#7899;c m&igrave;nh theo m&#7843;ng front-end nh&#432;ng ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng nh&#7853;n ra kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; h&#7913;ng th&uacute; n&ecirc;n d&#7847;n d&agrave; chuy&#7875;n sang back-end t&#7915; l&uacute;c n&agrave;o kh&ocirc;ng hay, v&agrave; [&hellip;]</div>";s:7:"content";s:14467:"<div><p class="p1"><strong><em><span class="s1">Th&#7921;c s&#7921; th&igrave; m&igrave;nh ch&#7881; m&#7899;i &#273;i l&agrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7847;n 1 n&#259;m, skill c&#361;ng ch&#432;a c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u n&ecirc;n c&#361;ng kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; ch&eacute;m gi&oacute; s&acirc;u v&agrave;o k&#7929; thu&#7853;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c. L&uacute;c tr&#432;&#7899;c m&igrave;nh theo m&#7843;ng front-end nh&#432;ng ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng nh&#7853;n ra kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; h&#7913;ng th&uacute; n&ecirc;n d&#7847;n d&agrave; chuy&#7875;n sang back-end t&#7915; l&uacute;c n&agrave;o kh&ocirc;ng hay, v&agrave; m&igrave;nh ch&#7881; c&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7889; l&#7901;i khuy&ecirc;n d&agrave;nh cho l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh website ch&#7913; b&ecirc;n &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng th&igrave; m&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng bi&#7871;t.</span></em></strong></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">K&#7929; n&#259;ng c&#7847;n h&#7885;c th&igrave; qu&aacute; nhi&#7873;u, m&#7895;i c&ocirc;ng ty c&oacute; m&#7895;i y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u v&agrave; thay &#273;&#7893;i theo th&#7901;i gian. K&#7929; thu&#7853;t ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n kh&ocirc;ng ng&#7915;ng n&ecirc;n m&#7897;t khi &#273;&atilde; theo ng&agrave;nh n&agrave;y th&igrave; x&aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh l&agrave; ph&#7843;i h&#7885;c c&#7843; &#273;&#7901;i.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">T&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i s&#7869; c&oacute; th&#7875; ch&eacute;m em r&#7857;ng &ocirc;i ch&uacute; em m&#7899;i &#273;i l&agrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7897;t n&#259;m th&igrave; bi&#7871;t g&igrave; v&#7873; k&#7929; thu&#7853;t m&agrave; n&oacute;i! Ahihi, c&#432;&#7901;i tr&#7915;. Th&#7921;c ra th&igrave; tr&igrave;nh &#273;&#7897; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; c&acirc;n &#273;o &#273;ong &#273;&#7871;m b&#7857;ng s&#7889; n&#259;m kinh nghi&#7879;m, ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&agrave; s&#7889; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; m&igrave;nh &#273;&atilde; g&#7863;p qua v&agrave; c&aacute;ch gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t n&oacute;, s&#7889; d&#7921; &aacute;n &#273;&atilde; ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh, b&aacute;c t&#7921; h&#7885;c bao nhi&ecirc;u gi&#7901; m&#7897;t ng&agrave;y, t&#7915; &#273;&oacute; r&uacute;t ra k&#7929; n&#259;ng c&#7911;a b&aacute;c c&oacute; c&#7913;ng kh&ocirc;ng. Ch&#7913; c&ograve;n n&oacute;i &ldquo;T&ocirc;i c&oacute; 5-6 n&#259;m experience nh&#432;ng trong 5-6 n&#259;m &#273;&oacute; to&agrave;n l&agrave;m xo&agrave;ng xo&agrave;ng, d&#7921; &aacute;n th&igrave; xong nh&#432;ng ki&#7875;u &#273;&uacute;ng deadline kh&ocirc;ng h&#417;n kh&ocirc;ng k&eacute;m, v&agrave; chi&#7873;u chi&#7873;u canh h&#7871;t gi&#7901; l&agrave;m r&#7891;i v&#7873;&rdquo;&hellip;. ch&#7845;m h&#7871;t, kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; &#273;&aacute;nh gi&aacute; ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c v&#7899;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p nh&#432; v&#7853;y.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Th&ocirc;i v&ocirc; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; ch&iacute;nh, v&#7853;y &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh th&igrave; c&#7847;n nh&#7919;ng g&igrave;, l&#7897; tr&igrave;nh th&#7871; n&agrave;o&hellip;.. C&aacute;i &#273;&oacute; ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o h&#432;&#7899;ng b&#7841;n &#273;i.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-11309" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-03-at-8.59.18-AM.png" alt="screen-shot-2016-11-03-at-8-59-18-am" width="586" height="622" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-03-at-8.59.18-AM.png 586w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-03-at-8.59.18-AM-283x300.png 283w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-03-at-8.59.18-AM-396x420.png 396w" sizes="(max-width: 586px) 100vw, 586px"></p>
<h3 class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>H&#432;&#7899;ng front-end developer</b></span></h3>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">H&#432;&#7899;ng n&agrave;y c&oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u k&#7929; thu&#7853;t, nh&#432;ng m&igrave;nh ngh&#297; c&aacute;c b&#7841;n n&ecirc;n h&#7885;c nh&#7919;ng k&#7929; thu&#7853;t ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n c&#7847;n tr&#432;&#7899;c. C&ograve;n l&#7841;i ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o c&ocirc;ng ty c&aacute;c b&#7841;n l&agrave;m c&oacute; y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u h&#7885;c th&ecirc;m kh&ocirc;ng. Danh s&aacute;ch th&igrave; d&agrave;i &#273;&#7857;ng &#273;&#7859;ng nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;y &#273;&acirc;y: <a href="https://github.com/dypsilon/frontend-dev-bookmarks"><span class="s2">https://github.com/dypsilon/frontend-dev-bookmarks</span></a></span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">Nh&#432;ng c&aacute;c skill sau &#273;&acirc;y nh&#7845;t &#273;&#7883;nh ph&#7843;i c&oacute; khi &#273;i l&agrave;m, &iacute;t nh&#7845;t l&agrave; &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c vi&#7879;c:</span></p>
<ul class="ul1"><li class="li2"><span class="s1">HTML (HTML5 c&agrave;ng t&#7889;t)</span></li>
<li class="li2"><span class="s1">CSS (CSS3 c&agrave;ng t&#7889;t)</span></li>
<li class="li2"><span class="s1">Javascript c&#417; b&#7843;n (jQuery). N&oacute;i tr&#432;&#7899;c l&agrave; Javascript chuy&ecirc;n s&acirc;u r&#7845;t hay v&agrave; r&#7845;t kh&oacute; g&#7863;m.</span></li>
<li class="li2"><span class="s1">Photoshop c&#417; b&#7843;n</span></li>
<li class="li2"><span class="s1">Illustrator c&#417; b&#7843;n</span></li>
<li class="li2"><span class="s1">M&#7897;t s&#7889; front-end framework nh&#432; Twitter Bootstrap, AngularJS m&#7899;i n&#7893;i&hellip;.</span></li>
</ul><h3 class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>H&#432;&#7899;ng back-end developer</b></span></h3>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">H&#432;&#7899;ng n&agrave;y th&igrave; kinh t&#7903;m h&#417;n, theo m&igrave;nh n&#7871;u &#273;&atilde; ch&#7885;n con &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ch&ocirc;ng gai n&agrave;y th&igrave; ch&#7881; n&ecirc;n ch&#7885;n 1-2 ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh m&agrave; theo (h&#7885;c s&acirc;u). M&igrave;nh th&agrave; l&agrave;m vua m&#7897;t n&#432;&#7899;c ch&#7913; n&#432;&#7899;c n&agrave;o c&#361;ng th&iacute;ch th&igrave; d&#7877; t&#7849;u h&#7887;a khi luy&#7879;n c&ocirc;ng l&#7855;m. C&aacute;c k&#7929; n&#259;ng c&#7847;n ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&agrave; n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng v&agrave; ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o t&#432; duy logic c&#7911;a b&#7841;n:</span></p>
<ul class="ul1"><li class="li2"><span class="s1">C&aacute;c n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng c&#417; b&#7843;n v&#7873; ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; b&#7841;n &#273;&#7883;nh l&agrave;m, m&#7845;y ki&#7871;n th&#7913;c &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n n&agrave;y ph&#7843;i kh&#7855;c c&#7889;t ghi t&acirc;m ch&#7913; &#273;&ocirc;i khi c&#361;ng c&oacute; ng&#432;&#7901;i qu&ecirc;n v&agrave; ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7885;c l&#7841;i t&#7915; Google. V&ograve;ng l&#7863;p, c&aacute;ch khai b&aacute;o bi&#7871;n, h&agrave;m, h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng&hellip;.. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t ph&#7887;ng v&#7845;n bao gi&#7901; c&#361;ng c&oacute; h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng.</span></li>
<li class="li2"><span class="s1">Ki&#7871;n th&#7913;c v&#7873; database MySQL, Microsoft SQL.</span></li>
<li class="li2"><span class="s1">R&#7897;ng h&#417;n l&agrave; Design Pattern (Singleton, Factory, Strategy, MVC, HMVC&hellip;.).</span></li>
<li class="li2"><span class="s1">C&aacute;c framework hot t&iacute;nh t&#7841;i th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m vi&#7871;t b&agrave;i n&agrave;y, &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n nh&#7845;t v&agrave; d&#7877; nh&#7845;t l&agrave; CodeIgniter.</span></li>
</ul><p class="p2"><span class="s1">B&#7841;n n&ecirc;n h&#7885;c m&#7897;t framework sau &#273;&oacute; &#273;i l&agrave;m v&agrave; h&#7885;c ti&#7871;p theo &#273;&#7875; d&#7877; th&#7845;m v&agrave; c&oacute; c&#417; h&#7897;i l&agrave;m nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n. Theo l&#7901;i khuy&ecirc;n c&#7911;a m&#7845;y &#273;&agrave;n anh &#273;i tr&#432;&#7899;c th&igrave; 1 developer c&#7847;n bi&#7871;t 2 framework v&agrave; 1 CMS n&#7871;u mu&#7889;n &#273;i &#273;&aacute;nh d&#7921; &aacute;n v&#7899;i c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty outsource.</span></p>
<h3 class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>H&#432;&#7899;ng full stack</b></span></h3>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1">L&agrave; full-stack developer c&oacute; ngh&#297;a l&agrave; b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i c&#7903;i m&#7903; &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; m&#7899;i, c&oacute; hi&#7875;u bi&#7871;t s&acirc;u v&#7873; m&#7897;t v&agrave;i c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; v&agrave; ph&#7843;i c&oacute; s&#7921; hi&#7875;u bi&#7871;t v&#7873; c&aacute;ch m&#7897;t &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng web &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n t&#7915; m&#7897;t kh&aacute;i ni&#7879;m thi&#7871;t k&#7871; cho &#273;&#7871;n khi c&aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&atilde; ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh.</span></p>
<p class="p2"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-11310" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-03-at-9.00.03-AM.png" alt="screen-shot-2016-11-03-at-9-00-03-am" width="760" height="278" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-03-at-9.00.03-AM.png 760w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-03-at-9.00.03-AM-300x110.png 300w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-03-at-9.00.03-AM-696x255.png 696w" sizes="(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px"></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Full-stack developer kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; ngh&#297;a l&agrave; ph&#7843;i th&ocirc;ng th&#7841;o m&#7885;i c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; m&agrave; ch&#7881; c&#7847;n c&oacute; hi&#7875;u bi&#7871;t v&#7873; c&aacute;c ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; &#273;ang c&oacute;, c&oacute; th&#7875; giao ti&#7871;p m&#7897;t c&aacute;ch th&ocirc;ng minh gi&#7919;a c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n trong nh&oacute;m v&agrave; l&agrave; m&#7897;t ngu&#7891;n l&#7921;c t&#7889;t, s&#7861;n s&agrave;ng n&#7871;u d&#7921; &aacute;n c&#7847;n &#273;&#7871;n b&#7841;n.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Full-stack tr&ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i hi&#7879;n nay c&oacute; th&#7875; c&#7847;n nh&#7919;ng k&#7929; n&#259;ng sau (tham kh&#7843;o):</span></p>
<ul class="ul1"><li class="li1"><span class="s1">Kh&ocirc;ng gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n m&igrave;nh &#7903; b&#7845;t k&#7923; 1 language hay 1 framework hay 1 chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n c&#7909; th&#7875; n&agrave;o.</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">C&oacute; ki&#7871;n th&#7913;c IT t&#7893;ng qu&aacute;t v&agrave; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng t&igrave;m hi&#7875;u s&acirc;u khi c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t b&#7845;t k&#7923; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; g&igrave; thu&#7897;c: (1) Server &ndash; Network (2) Database (3) Web frameworks (4) Mobile frameworks</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">Hi&#7875;u v&agrave; &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c UI/UX v&agrave;o trong projects</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">N&#7855;m b&#7855;t nhanh Business Logics v&agrave; chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&agrave;nh Technical Logics</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">Bi&#7871;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c khi n&agrave;o c&#7847;n hi&#7875;u r&#7897;ng, khi n&agrave;o c&#7847;n hi&#7875;u s&acirc;u m&#7897;t v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873;</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">C&oacute; th&#7875; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &iacute;t nh&#7845;t 1 ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh web v&agrave; 1 ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh mobile (iOS/Android)</span></li>
</ul><p class="p1"><span class="s1">Hi&#7879;n nay kh&aacute; nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i theo h&#432;&#7899;ng n&agrave;y, m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n do c&aacute;i danh full-stack kh&aacute; l&agrave; hay ho (c&#7843;m gi&aacute;c nh&#432; super hero), m&#7897;t ph&#7847;n l&agrave; hi&#7879;n nay c&aacute;c nh&agrave; tuy&#7875;n d&#7909;ng c&#361;ng y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u kh&aacute; cao v&#7873; skills c&#7911;a developer. C&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; ch&#7871;t ti&#7879;t trong th&#7871; gi&#7899;i l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh l&#7895;i th&#7901;i &#273;&#7911; nhanh &#273;&#7875; cu&#7889;n tr&ocirc;i b&#7845;t k&#7923; 1 &ldquo;n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng&rdquo; v&#7919;ng ch&atilde;i n&agrave;o. Do &#273;&oacute; n&#7871;u b&#7841;n ch&#7881; bi&#7871;t 1 ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919;, bi&#7871;t 1 n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng n&agrave;o &#273;&oacute;, hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i b&#7841;n v&#7851;n c&oacute; th&#7875; ki&#7873;m ti&#7873;n ngon &#259;n v&#7899;i n&oacute;, nh&#432;ng li&#7879;u 2 &ndash; 4 n&#259;m n&#7919;a th&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Do &#273;&oacute; b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; l&agrave; 1 &ldquo;super-code d&#7841;o&rdquo; hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i, nh&#432;ng ch&#432;a ch&#7855;c &#273;i&#7873;u &#273;&oacute; s&#7869; &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o cho b&#7841;n m&#7897;t t&#432;&#417;ng lai ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n cho nh&#7919;ng n&#259;m t&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;u.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">&#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i ai &#273;i theo h&#432;&#7899;ng n&agrave;y, n&#7871;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c n&ecirc;n h&#7885;c front-end tr&#432;&#7899;c r&#7891;i t&#7915; t&#7915; m&ograve; qua back-end b&#7903;i v&igrave; trong 1 n&#259;m b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; n&agrave;o tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh full-stack &#273;&acirc;u &ndash; c&#361;ng c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i t&#7921; phong, ahihi. V&agrave; t&#7845;t nhi&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh c&#361;ng khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch (n&#7871;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c) c&aacute;c b&#7841;n n&ecirc;n &#273;i theo h&#432;&#7899;ng n&agrave;y (v&#7873; l&acirc;u v&#7873; d&agrave;i) &#273;&#7875; &#273;&aacute;p &#7913;ng nhu c&#7847;u c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c trong t&#432;&#417;ng lai.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">T&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t m&igrave;nh &#273;&atilde; n&ecirc;u &#7903; tr&ecirc;n, n&#7871;u c&aacute;c b&#7841;n bi&#7871;t v&#7873; ch&uacute;ng th&igrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;i code d&#7841;o v&agrave; ki&#7871;m c&#417;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c r&#7891;i. Sau n&agrave;y &#273;i l&agrave;m c&#7889; g&#7855;ng trau d&#7891;i nhi&#7873;u th&#7853;t nhi&#7873;u k&#7929; n&#259;ng &#273;&#7875; t&#259;ng gi&aacute; tr&#7883; b&#7843;n th&acirc;n l&ecirc;n (t&#259;ng l&#432;&#417;ng).</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em>Techtalk via <a href="https://jusfunny.wordpress.com/2016/04/18/lap-trinh-web-nen-hoc-gi-day/">justfunny</a></em></span></p>
<p class="p2"></p></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";s:7:"Hieu Le";s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";N;}s:4:"date";s:19:"2016-11-07 03:00:02";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:78:"Rails vẫn là sự lựa chọn hoàn hảo khi học lập trình năm 2016";s:4:"link";s:84:"http://techtalk.vn/rails-van-la-su-lua-chon-hoan-hao-khi-hoc-lap-trinh-nam-2016.html";s:11:"description";s:581:"<div>Rails &#273;&atilde; v&agrave; &#273;ang &#273;&#7913;ng trong h&agrave;ng ng&#361; c&aacute;c ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u trong h&#417;n 12 n&#259;m qua. V&agrave; 12 n&#259;m trong gi&#7899;i c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; c&#361;ng g&#7847;n b&#7857;ng v&#7899;i b&#7845;t t&#7917;, v&igrave; nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;i t&ecirc;n c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; c&#361;ng s&#7889;ng ng&#7847;n &#7845;y n&#259;m l&agrave; v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng &iacute;t &#7887;i. Nh&#432; m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&atilde; bi&#7871;t, n&#7873;n c&ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p [&hellip;]</div>";s:7:"content";s:16240:"<div><p>Rails &#273;&atilde; v&agrave; &#273;ang &#273;&#7913;ng trong h&agrave;ng ng&#361; c&aacute;c ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7847;u trong h&#417;n 12 n&#259;m qua. V&agrave; 12 n&#259;m trong gi&#7899;i c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; c&#361;ng g&#7847;n b&#7857;ng v&#7899;i b&#7845;t t&#7917;, v&igrave; nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;i t&ecirc;n c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; c&#361;ng s&#7889;ng ng&#7847;n &#7845;y n&#259;m l&agrave; v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng &iacute;t &#7887;i.</p>
<p>Nh&#432; m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&atilde; bi&#7871;t, n&#7873;n c&ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m thay &#273;&#7893;i v&#7899;i t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng, &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t trong l&#297;nh v&#7921;c web, v&#7853;y v&igrave; l&yacute; do n&agrave;o m&agrave; Rails c&oacute; th&#7875; tr&#7909; v&#7919;ng l&acirc;u nh&#432; v&#7853;y? C&oacute; c&aacute;ch n&agrave;o ta v&#7851;n d&ugrave;ng Rails l&agrave;m web framework &#273;&#432;&#7907;c kh&ocirc;ng? &Yacute; t&ocirc;i l&agrave;, v&#7899;i Concurrent n&agrave;y r&#7891;i Functional kia lu&ocirc;n lu&ocirc;n th&#7889;ng tr&#7883; headlines, m&#7897;t th&#7913; framework d&#7921;a tr&ecirc;n ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng th&igrave; c&oacute; g&igrave; m&agrave; &#273;&aacute;ng h&#7885;c?</p>
<p>&#272;&oacute; l&agrave; c&acirc;u h&#7887;i h&ocirc;m nay ta s&#7869; tr&#7843; l&#7901;i. Rails v&#7851;n c&ograve;n r&#7845;t &#273;&aacute;ng h&#7885;c.</p>
<h2><b>Doctrine v&agrave; Vision</b></h2>
<p>Rails c&oacute; m&#7897;t <i>doctrine</i>. Th&#7853;t s&#7921; c&oacute; &#273;&#7845;y. &#7902; ngay <a href="http://rubyonrails.org/doctrine/">&#273;&acirc;y</a> n&agrave;y. T&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng bi&#7871;t c&aacute;c b&#7841;n th&#7871; n&agrave;o, nh&#432;ng m&#7895;i khi t&ocirc;i th&#7845;y Doctrine <i>such </i>v&agrave; <i>such</i>, t&ocirc;i l&#7841;i ngh&#297; ngay &#273;&#7871;n m&#7845;y con chu&#7897;t lang b&#7883; &eacute;p l&agrave;m n&ocirc; l&#7879; b&#7903;i m&#7897;t t&ecirc;n &#273;&#7897;c t&agrave;i hoang t&#432;&#7903;ng n&agrave;o &#273;&oacute;. Ch&#7855;c l&agrave; do t&ocirc;i &#273;&#7885;c m&#7845;y truy&#7879;n vi&#7877;n t&#432;&#7903;ng gi&#7853;t g&acirc;n h&acirc;u kh&#7843;i huy&#7873;n nhi&#7873;u qu&aacute; r&#7891;i. Rails Doctrine, tuy v&#7853;y v&#7851;n ch&#7841;y t&#7889;t ch&aacute;n. Sau &#273;&acirc;y l&agrave; m&#7897;t v&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n t&#7855;c:</p>
<ul><li>T&#7889;i &#432;u cho l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh h&#7841;nh ph&uacute;c &ndash; Optimize for programmer happiness</li>
<li>Quy &#432;&#7899;c v&#432;&#7907;t tr&ecirc;n c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh &ndash; Convention over Configuration</li>
<li>Menu l&agrave; omakase (t&#7845;t c&#7843; ph&#7909; thu&#7897;c v&agrave;o &lsquo;&#273;&#7847;u b&#7871;p&rsquo;) &ndash; The menu is omakase</li>
<li>Kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; m&#7897;t ki&#7875;u m&#7851;u &ndash; No one paradigm</li>
<li>&#272;&#7873; cao code &lsquo;&#273;&#7865;p&rsquo; &ndash; Exalt beautiful code</li>
<li>Cung c&#7845;p &lsquo;dao k&eacute;o&rsquo; s&#7855;c b&eacute;n &ndash; Provide sharp knives</li>
<li>H&#7879; th&#7889;ng t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p gi&aacute; tr&#7883; &ndash; Value integrated systems</li>
<li>Ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897; cao h&#417;n &#273;&#7897; &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh &ndash; Progress over stability</li>
<li>&#272;&#7849;y &lsquo;l&#7873;u&rsquo; &ndash; Push up a big tent</li>
</ul><p>Hi&#7879;n t&ocirc;i s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng &#273;i qua t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng nguy&ecirc;n t&#7855;c n&agrave;y, nh&#432;ng t&ocirc;i ngh&#297; l&agrave; b&#7841;n n&ecirc;n t&igrave;m &#273;&#7885;c. B&#7841;n bi&#7871;t h&#7885; kh&ocirc;ng th&#7921;c s&#7921; n&oacute;i nh&#7919;ng g&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng? &ldquo;Make a website&rdquo;. Danh s&aacute;ch ch&#7913;a &#273;&#7847;y nh&#7919;ng t&#7915; nh&#432; &ldquo;h&#7841;nh ph&uacute;c&rdquo;, &ldquo;&#273;&#7865;p&rdquo;, &ldquo;ti&#7871;n &#273;&#7897;&rdquo;, &ldquo;gi&aacute; tr&#7883;&rdquo;. C&aacute;i n&agrave;y l&agrave; cho <i>web framework</i>.</p>
<p>&#272;&acirc;y ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng nguy&ecirc;n t&#7855;c hay v&agrave; &#273;&aacute;ng tu&acirc;n theo cho b&#7845;t c&#7913; c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n n&agrave;o. Ch&uacute;ng &#273;&#7883;nh h&igrave;nh h&#432;&#7899;ng &#273;i c&#7911;a framework v&agrave; c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng xung quanh &#273;&oacute;. Tuy c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7841;n s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#7891;ng &yacute; v&#7899;i t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng nguy&ecirc;n t&#7855;c tr&ecirc;n, nh&#432;ng &iacute;t nh&#7845;t b&#7841;n bi&#7871;t ch&uacute;ng l&agrave; g&igrave;.</p>
<p>B&#7845;t c&#7913; framework n&agrave;o &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; nhi&#7873;u c&ocirc;ng s&#7913;c nh&#432; v&#7853;y v&agrave;o c&aacute;c nguy&ecirc;n t&#7855;c chi ph&#7889;i m&igrave;nh, th&igrave; &#7855;t ph&#7843;i th&#7853;t tr&#432;&#7903;ng th&agrave;nh v&agrave; th&ocirc;ng minh. T&ocirc;i r&#7845;t th&iacute;ch nh&#7919;ng nguy&ecirc;n t&#7855;c n&agrave;y v&agrave; t&ocirc;i hi&#7875;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, nh&#7919;ng nguy&ecirc;n t&#7855;c n&agrave;y t&#7891;n t&#7841;i nh&#7857;m gi&uacute;p nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i nh&#432; t&ocirc;i c&oacute; th&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; n&agrave;y tho&#7843;i m&aacute;i v&agrave; d&#7877; d&agrave;ng h&#417;n.</p>
<h2><b>Th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nhanh ch&oacute;ng<br></b></h2>
<p><img class="size-full aligncenter" src="https://dab1nmslvvntp.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/1477490659Fotolia_62573480_Subscription_Monthly_M-300x300.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="300"></p>
<p>C&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; th&#7853;t t&#7915; l&acirc;u m&agrave; ai c&#361;ng bi&#7871;t l&agrave;, Rails cho ph&eacute;p developer &lsquo;t&#259;ng t&#7889;c&rsquo; ngay t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng gi&acirc;y ph&uacute;t &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n th&#7913; g&igrave; &#273;&oacute; nhanh, nh&#432; khi mu&#7889;n &ldquo;th&#7917; nghi&#7879;m l&yacute; thuy&#7871;t&rdquo; ch&#7859;ng h&#7841;n, b&#7841;n s&#7869; kh&oacute; l&ograve;ng t&igrave;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; n&agrave;o ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p nh&#432; Rails &#273;&acirc;u. B&#7903;i l&#7869; &#273;&oacute;, Rails &#273;&atilde; tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n s&#7889; m&#7897;t cho v&ocirc; v&agrave;n startup.</p>
<p>Nh&#432;ng m&agrave;, &#273;&acirc;y kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; cho startup. Khi b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n h&#7885;c th&#7913; c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; g&igrave; m&#7899;i, th&#432;&#7901;ng s&#7869; m&#7845;t r&#7845;t l&acirc;u &#273;&#7875; b&#7841;n h&#7885;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7913; g&igrave; &#273;&oacute; ra h&#7891;n. B&#7841;n ph&#7843;i v&#432;&#7907;t qua m&#7897;t tr&igrave;nh &#273;&#7897; n&agrave;o &#273;&oacute;, nh&#432; <code>newbie</code> ch&#7859;ng h&#7841;n, &#273;&#7875; d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c. R&#7845;t kh&oacute; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n m&#7897;t cam k&#7871;t nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;y khi b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i th&#432;&#7901;ng xuy&ecirc;n chuy&#7875;n ngh&#7873; ho&#7863;c c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m kh&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n vai. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n c&ograve;n kh&aacute; m&#7899;i v&#7899;i gi&#7899;i l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh, Rails s&#7869; cho b&#7841;n nh&#7919;ng th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng t&#7915; s&#7899;m. T&#7915; r&#7845;t r&#7845;t s&#7899;m l&agrave; &#273;&#7857;ng kh&aacute;c. B&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i h&#7885;c <i>c&#7843; </i>m&#7897;t ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh, m&agrave; ch&#7881; v&#7915;a &#273;&#7911; &#273;&#7875; nh&#7843;y ra th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng m&agrave; th&ocirc;i. Th&#7921;c ra, c&oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#7871;n v&#7899;i Ruby th&ocirc;ng qua Rails, &#273;&#7871;n m&#7913;c Rail b&#7883; t&#432;&#7903;ng nh&#7847;m l&agrave; Ruby lu&ocirc;n.</p>
<p>H&atilde;y h&#7885;c Rails v&igrave; b&#7841;n s&#7869; c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7845;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ti&#7873;n b&#7897; ngay. V&agrave; s&#7921; ti&#7871;n b&#7897; &#273;&oacute; s&#7869; th&ocirc;i th&uacute;c b&#7841;n h&#7885;c ti&#7871;p.</p>
<h2><b>H&#7885;c lu&ocirc;n c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m web<br></b></h2>
<p>M&#7897;t kh&iacute;a c&#7841;nh n&#7919;a c&#7911;a Rails l&agrave; ki&#7875;u c&aacute;ch &lsquo;th&#7847;n ch&uacute;, nh&#7883;p nh&agrave;ng&rsquo;, do ng&#432;&#7901;i t&#7841;o v&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#7873;u &ldquo;Convention Over Configuration&rdquo;. C&oacute; ngh&#297;a l&agrave;, v&#7873; c&#417; b&#7843;n, Rails &#273;&atilde; ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n giao th&#7913;c (c&aacute;ch th&#7913;c l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c) gi&#7843; &#273;&#7883;nh m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh nh&#7845;t &#273;&#7883;nh. V&iacute; d&#7909;, b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t database khi b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u v&#7899;i Rails. Rails s&#7869; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng SQLite theo <i>quy &#432;&#7899;c</i> n&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh m&#7897;t database kh&aacute;c. B&ecirc;n c&#7841;nh minh ch&#7913;ng cho &lsquo;th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng ch&#7899;p nho&aacute;ng&rsquo; ta &#273;&atilde; n&oacute;i &#7903; tr&ecirc;n, ta c&ograve;n th&#7845;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c <i>web l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;o</i>.</p>
<p>Khoan &#273;&atilde;, t&ocirc;i n&oacute;i th&#7871; ngh&#297;a l&agrave; sao &#7845;y nh&#7881;? &Agrave; th&igrave;, &yacute; t&ocirc;i l&agrave; &#273;a s&#7889; website c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i l&#432;u tr&#7919; d&#7919; li&#7879;u, n&ecirc;n Rails c&#361;ng c&oacute; quy &#432;&#7899;c cho vi&#7879;c &#273;&oacute; lu&ocirc;n. &#272;&#7841;i &#273;a s&#7889; &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng web ngo&agrave;i kia s&#7917; d&#7909;ng chu&#7849;n x&aacute;c minh theo session, v&#7853;y n&ecirc;n Rails c&#361;ng c&oacute; quy &#432;&#7899;c cho vi&#7879;c n&agrave;y. Khi b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; bi&#7871;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7919;ng quy &#432;&#7899;c n&agrave;y, b&#7841;n c&#361;ng bi&#7871;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c lu&ocirc;n &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng web c&#7847;n c&oacute; nh&#7919;ng g&igrave;. Sau &#273;&acirc;y l&agrave; v&iacute; d&#7909; minh h&#7885;a:</p>
<ul><li>RESTful endpoints</li>
<li>Asset compression and building</li>
<li>Database migrations</li>
<li>Package and dependency management</li>
<li>Testing</li>
</ul><p>C&ograve;n nhi&#7873;u n&#7919;a, nh&#432;ng b&#7841;n c&#361;ng n&#7855;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng r&#7891;i &#273;&#7845;y. B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; l&#7845;y l&#7841;i y nguy&ecirc;n danh s&aacute;ch tr&ecirc;n v&agrave; ch&#7881; c&#7847;n ch&#7881;nh nh&#7865; l&#7841;i m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&#7845;u h&igrave;nh n&#7871;u c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t. B&#7841;n c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7887; lu&ocirc;n, ho&#7863;c thay th&#7871; nh&#7919;ng quy &#432;&#7899;c n&agrave;y v&#7899;i gems ho&#7863;c code c&#7911;a ch&iacute;nh m&igrave;nh. Khi &#273;&atilde; s&#7861;n s&agrave;ng, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&agrave;o s&acirc;u h&#417;n v&agrave;o m&#7895;i quy &#432;&#7899;c v&agrave; t&igrave;m hi&#7875;u t&#7841;i sao ch&uacute;ng l&#7841;i t&#7891;n t&#7841;i. Qua nhi&#7873;u l&#7847;n ng&#7909;p l&#7863;n s&acirc;u h&#417;n nh&#432; th&#7871; n&agrave;y, b&#7841;n s&#7869; h&#7885;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nhi&#7873;u &#273;i&#7873;u n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng v&#7873; qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&agrave; tri&#7875;n khai &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng web. H&#417;n th&#7871; n&#7919;a, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; d&ugrave;ng quy &#432;&#7899;c cho &#273;&#7871;n khi &#273;&atilde; s&#7861;n s&agrave;ng, h&#7885;c t&#7853;p theo t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p m&agrave; v&#7851;n cho ra &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng web d&ugrave;ng t&#7889;t.</p>
<h2><a href="http://techtalk.vn/dung-tren-vai-nguoi-khong-lo.html"><b>&#272;&#7913;ng tr&ecirc;n vai ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&#7893;ng l&#7891;</b></a></h2>
<p>Rails &#273;&atilde; cho ra nhi&#7873;u g&atilde; kh&#7895;ng l&#7891; trong ng&agrave;nh ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n web. Rails ra &#273;&#7901;i l&agrave; framework &#273;&#7875; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng <a href="http://basecamp.com/">Basecamp</a>, m&#7897;t d&#7883;ch v&#7909; r&#7845;t th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng v&#7899;i traffic c&#7921;c cao th&#7901;i &#273;&oacute;. Nh&#432; v&#7853;y &#273;&#7891;ng ngh&#297;a v&#7899;i vi&#7879;c nh&#7919;ng v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng trang web g&#7889;c data, traffic cao nh&#432; Basecamp &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t, v&agrave; ta ch&#7881; vi&#7879;c g&#7863;t h&aacute;i nh&#7919;ng th&agrave;nh qu&#7843; &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7841;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&ocirc;i.</p>
<p>Trong 12 n&#259;m, Rails &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &aacute;p d&#7909;ng v&agrave;o nhi&#7873;u trang r&#7845;t th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng. Nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i tham gia x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng nh&#7919;ng trang n&agrave;y &#273;&atilde; cho ra nhi&#7873;u gem ngu&#7891;n tuy&#7879;t v&#7901;i &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t c&aacute;c v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; h&#7885; g&#7863;p ph&#7843;i. M&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng v&iacute; d&#7909; &#273;i&#7875;n h&igrave;nh nh&#7845;t l&agrave; <a href="https://github.com/plataformatec/devise">Devise</a>, gem de facto &#273;&#7875; x&aacute;c minh trong Rails. Khi s&#7917; d&#7909;ng Devise (v&agrave; c&aacute;c gem kh&aacute;c), b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; cho ph&eacute;p ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng x&aacute;c minh theo r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;c nhau. Email/password, Twitter, Facebook, Github, JWT,&hellip; Devise ch&#7881; l&agrave; m&#7897;t trong h&agrave;ng ngh&igrave;n v&iacute; d&#7909; ngo&agrave;i kia m&agrave; th&ocirc;i.</p>
<p>Rails &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng b&#7903;i ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&#7893;ng l&#7891; v&agrave; c&#361;ng do nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&#7893;ng l&#7891; kh&aacute;c ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n.</p>
<h2><b>Anh v&agrave; &#273;&#7897;i qu&acirc;n n&agrave;o c&#417;?<br></b></h2>
<p>Khi b&#7841;n b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u l&#7863;n ng&#7909;p v&agrave;o Rails c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng n&agrave;y c&#361;ng s&#7869; tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh c&#7897;ng &#273;&#7891;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n, N&#7871;u b&#7841;n truy c&#7853;p v&agrave;o <a href="http://rubygems.org/">Rubygems</a> v&agrave; <a href="https://rubygems.org/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&amp;query=rail://rubygems.org/search?utf8=%E2%9C%93&amp;query=rails">t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m &ldquo;rails</a>&rdquo;. B&#7841;n s&#7869; th&#7845;y k&#7871;t qu&#7843; c&#7905; kho&#7843;ng&hellip; 160 trang gem. 160 trang c&#417; &#273;&#7845;y!! v&agrave; lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; gem m&#7899;i xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n m&#7895;i tu&#7847;n.</p>
<p>H&#417;n n&#7919;a, ngu&#7891;n t&agrave;i li&#7879;u Rails tr&ecirc;n internet nhi&#7873;u v&ocirc; s&#7889;. V&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u forum nh&#432; Sitepoint hay Stackoverflow &#273;&#7875; h&#7887;i han &#273;&#7911; th&#7913;. R&#7891;i c&ograve;n Slack group. N&oacute;i t&oacute;m l&#7841;i, lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; m&#7897;t &ldquo;&#273;&#7841;i &#273;&#7897;i 500 anh em&rdquo; t&uacute;c tr&#7921;c gi&uacute;p &#273;&#7905; b&#7841;n m&#7885;i v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; v&#7873; Rails.</p>
<h2><b>Ruby tuy&#7879;t &#273;&#7865;p<br></b></h2>
<p>Theo t&ocirc;i, m&#7897;t trong nh&#7919;ng l&yacute; do thuy&#7871;t ph&#7909;c nh&#7845;t n&ecirc;n h&#7885;c Rails l&agrave; v&igrave; ch&iacute;nh Ruby, &#273;&acirc;y l&agrave; m&#7897;t th&#7913; ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; tuy&#7879;t &#273;&#7865;p.</p>
<p>Trong m&#7897;t b&agrave;i vi&#7871;t h&#7891;i nh&#7919;ng ng&agrave;y tu&#7893;i &#273;&#7847;u c&#7911;a Ruby, Yukihiro Matsumoto (cha &#273;&#7875; c&#7911;a Ruby) t&#7915;ng vi&#7871;t &ldquo;&hellip;Ruby &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; &#273;&#7875; mang l&#7841;i h&#7841;nh ph&uacute;c cho l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n&rdquo;. V&agrave; &ocirc;ng &#273;&atilde; l&agrave;m r&#7845;t t&#7889;t, gi&#7919; cho Ruby &#273;i theo s&#7913; m&#7879;nh n&agrave;y.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em>Techtalk via <a href="https://www.sitepoint.com/why-learning-rails-is-still-a-great-choice-in-2016/">Sitepoint</a></em></p></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Thien Bui";s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";N;}s:4:"date";s:19:"2016-11-07 01:00:40";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}}i:2;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:34:"More iPhone Development with Swift";s:4:"link";s:58:"http://techtalk.vn/more-iphone-development-with-swift.html";s:11:"description";s:45:"<div>T&#7843;i t&#7841;i &#273;&acirc;y</div>";s:7:"content";s:164:"<div><h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>T&#7843;i t&#7841;i <a href="http://slimshare.com/file/57f87b958c862b47318b4568">&#273;&acirc;y</a></strong></h3></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Thien Bui";s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";N;}s:4:"date";s:19:"2016-11-06 13:00:26";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}}i:3;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:79:"Giới thiệu kỹ thuật Long-Polling, Websockets, Server-Sent Events, Comet";s:4:"link";s:92:"http://techtalk.vn/gioi-thieu-ky-thuat-long-polling-websockets-server-sent-events-comet.html";s:11:"description";s:595:"<div>Hi&#7879;n nay &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng web &#273;&atilde; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n kh&aacute;c xa so v&#7899;i ng&agrave;y &#273;&#7847;u n&oacute; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n, k&egrave;m theo &#273;&oacute; l&agrave; v&ocirc; s&#7889; c&aacute;c k&#7929; thu&#7853;t m&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &aacute;p d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7875; ph&#7909;c v&#7909; cho qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y nh&#7857;m &#273;em l&#7841;i tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m m&#7899;i m&#7867;, &#273;&#7847;y h&#7913;ng th&uacute; v&agrave; c&#361;ng kh&ocirc;ng k&eacute;m ph&#7847;n ti&#7879;n d&#7909;ng cho [&hellip;]</div>";s:7:"content";s:14374:"<div><p>Hi&#7879;n nay &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng web &#273;&atilde; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n kh&aacute;c xa so v&#7899;i ng&agrave;y &#273;&#7847;u n&oacute; xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n, k&egrave;m theo &#273;&oacute; l&agrave; v&ocirc; s&#7889; c&aacute;c k&#7929; thu&#7853;t m&#7899;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &aacute;p d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7875; ph&#7909;c v&#7909; cho qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y nh&#7857;m &#273;em l&#7841;i tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m m&#7899;i m&#7867;, &#273;&#7847;y h&#7913;ng th&uacute; v&agrave; c&#361;ng kh&ocirc;ng k&eacute;m ph&#7847;n ti&#7879;n d&#7909;ng cho ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng.</p>
<p>&#272;&#7875; c&aacute;c b&#7841;n c&oacute; 1 c&aacute;i nh&igrave;n r&otilde; r&agrave;ng h&#417;n v&#7873; c&ocirc;ng ngh&#7879; web hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, h&ocirc;m nay m&igrave;nh s&#7869; gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u v&#7899;i c&aacute;c b&#7841;n 1 s&#7889; k&#7929; thu&#7853;t hi&#7879;n nay th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng trong c&aacute;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng web th&#7901;i gian th&#7921;c.</p>
<p>(<em>Trong c&aacute;c v&iacute; d&#7909; b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i, m&aacute;y kh&aacute;ch (client) s&#7869; l&agrave; tr&igrave;nh duy&#7879;t c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng, server s&#7869; l&agrave; webserver hosting c&#7911;a website , b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i l&agrave; client v&agrave; b&ecirc;n ph&#7843;i l&agrave; server</em>). Tuy nhi&ecirc;n tr&#432;&#7899;c ti&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh s&#7869; gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh truy c&#7853;p theo giao th&#7913;c http truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng.</p>
<h2>Regular HTTP:</h2>
<ol><li>Ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng g&#7917;i y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u (request) 1 website t&#7915; m&#7897;t m&aacute;y ch&#7911;.</li>
<li>M&aacute;y ch&#7911; (server) t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n d&#7919; li&#7879;u tr&#7843; v&#7873; ( response ).</li>
<li>M&aacute;y ch&#7911; g&#7917;i d&#7919; li&#7879;u tr&#7843; v&#7873; (response) cho ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng (client).</li>
</ol><p>~&gt; Client ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng g&#7917;i request &#273;&#7871;n server th&igrave; s&#7869; c&oacute; response tr&#7843; v&#7873; cho client, c&ograve;n n&#7871;u ko c&oacute; request t&#7915; client th&igrave; server s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;m g&igrave; c&#7843;.</p>
<h2>AJAX Polling:</h2>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-11340" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-polling.png" alt="ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-polling" width="646" height="364" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-polling.png 646w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-polling-300x169.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 646px) 100vw, 646px"></p>
<ol><li>Client y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u 1 trang web t&#7915; server s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &ldquo;Regular http&rdquo; (&#273;&atilde; n&oacute;i &#7903; tr&ecirc;n).</li>
<li>Trang web m&agrave; client v&#7915;a y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u s&#7869; d&ugrave;ng javascript th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n request li&ecirc;n t&#7909;c &#273;&#7871;n 1 file tr&ecirc;n server trong m&#7897;t kho&#7843;ng th&#7901;i gian &#273;&#7873;u &#273;&#7863;n (v&iacute; d&#7909;: c&#7913; m&#7895;i 2 gi&acirc;y s&#7869; g&#7917;i 1 request &#273;&#7871;n server).</li>
<li>Server s&#7869; t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n response &#7913;ng v&#7899;i m&#7895;i request v&agrave; g&#7917;i l&#7841;i response cho client gi&#7889;ng nh&#432; giao th&#7913;c http truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng.</li>
</ol><p>~&gt; Client kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng g&#7917;i request &#273;&#7871;n server nh&#432;ng javascript c&#7911;a website v&#7851;n lu&acirc;n phi&ecirc;n g&#7917;i request &#273;&#7871;n server v&agrave; client s&#7869; nh&#7853;n response t&#7915; server 1 c&aacute;ch b&#7883; &#273;&#7897;ng.</p>
<h2>AJAX Long-Polling:</h2>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-11341" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-long-polling.png" alt="ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-long-polling" width="646" height="364" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-long-polling.png 646w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-long-polling-300x169.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 646px) 100vw, 646px"></p>
<ol><li>Client y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u 1 trang web t&#7915; server s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &ldquo;Regular http&rdquo; (&#273;&atilde; n&oacute;i &#7903; tr&ecirc;n).</li>
<li>Trang web m&agrave; client v&#7915;a y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u s&#7869; d&ugrave;ng javascript th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n request &#273;&#7871;n 1 file tr&ecirc;n server.</li>
<li>Server s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng g&#7917;i response ngay cho client (&#7913;ng v&#7899;i request &#273;&atilde; g&#7917;i) m&agrave; s&#7869; &#273;&#7907;i cho &#273;&#7871;n khi c&oacute; d&#7919; li&#7879;u m&#7899;i.</li>
<li>Khi c&oacute; d&#7919; li&#7879;u m&#7899;i, server s&#7869; g&#7917;i d&#7919; li&#7879;u m&#7899;i &#273;&oacute; (response) v&#7873; cho client.</li>
<li>Client sau khi nh&#7853;n d&#7919; li&#7879;u m&#7899;i t&#7915; server, ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c s&#7869; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c 1 request kh&aacute;c &#273;&#7871;n server &#273;&#7875; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u l&#7841;i to&agrave;n b&#7897; ti&#7871;n tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y (b&#432;&#7899;c 3 &#273;&#7871;n 5).</li>
</ol><p>~&gt; Client s&#7869; g&#7917;i request &#273;&#7871;n server, server ti&#7871;n h&agrave;nh ki&#7871;m tra d&#7919; li&#7879;u v&agrave; &#273;&#7871;n khi n&agrave;o c&oacute; d&#7919; li&#7879;u m&#7899;i th&igrave; m&#7899;i g&#7917;i response v&#7873; cho client. Sau &#273;&oacute; client l&#7841;i ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c t&#7921; &#273;&#7897;ng g&#7917;i 1 request m&#7899;i v&agrave; &#273;&#7907;i d&#7919; li&#7879;u m&#7899;i tr&#7843; v&#7873;.</p>
<h2>HTML5 Server Sent Events (SSE) / Event Source:</h2>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-11342" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-html5.png" alt="ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-html5" width="646" height="364" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-html5.png 646w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-html5-300x169.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 646px) 100vw, 646px"></p>
<ol><li>Client y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u 1 trang web t&#7915; server s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &ldquo;Regular http&rdquo; (&#273;&atilde; n&oacute;i &#7903; tr&ecirc;n).</li>
<li>Trang web m&agrave; client v&#7915;a y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u s&#7869; d&ugrave;ng javascript m&#7903; 1 k&#7871;t n&#7889;i &#273;&#7871;n server.</li>
<li>K&#7875; t&#7915; l&uacute;c n&agrave;y server s&#7869; g&#7917;i response tr&#7843; v&#7873; cho client m&#7895;i khi c&oacute; d&#7919; li&#7879;u m&#7899;i.</li>
</ol><p>~&gt; T&#7913;c l&agrave; client lu&ocirc;n nh&#7853;n d&#7919; li&#7879;u m&#7899;i theo th&#7901;i gian th&#7921;c t&#7915; server ch&#7881; v&#7899;i 1 l&#7847;n request (d&#7919; li&#7879;u 1 chi&#7873;u t&#7915; server &#273;&#7871;n client). L&uacute;c n&agrave;y tr&ecirc;n server s&#7869; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n 1 v&ograve;ng l&#7863;p (loop) s&#7921; ki&#7879;n (b&#432;&#7899;c 1 &#273;&#7871;n 3) &#273;&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n l&#7841;i nhi&#7873;u l&#7847;n quy tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y, tuy nhi&ecirc;n b&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; k&#7871;t n&#7889;i &#273;&#7871;n server t&#7915; 1 t&ecirc;n mi&#7873;n (domain) kh&aacute;c.</p>
<h2>HTML5 Websockets:</h2>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-11343" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-socket.png" alt="ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-socket" width="646" height="364" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-socket.png 646w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-socket-300x169.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 646px) 100vw, 646px"></p>
<ol><li>Client y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u 1 trang web t&#7915; server s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &ldquo;Regular http&rdquo; (&#273;&atilde; n&oacute;i &#7903; tr&ecirc;n).</li>
<li>Trang web m&agrave; client v&#7915;a y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u s&#7869; d&ugrave;ng javascript m&#7903; 1 k&#7871;t n&#7889;i &#273;&#7871;n server.</li>
<li>B&acirc;y gi&#7901; c&#7843; server v&agrave; client c&oacute; th&#7875; g&#7917;i nh&#7853;n nhi&#7873;u d&#7919; li&#7879;u kh&aacute;c nhau v&#7899;i nhau khi c&oacute; d&#7919; li&#7879;u m&#7899;i (gi&#7889;ng nh&#432; ki&#7875;u 2 b&ecirc;n &#273;ang chat v&#7899;i nhau ch&#7913; kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i tu&acirc;n theo qui t&#7855;c n&agrave;o).</li>
</ol><p>~&gt; T&#7913;c l&agrave; client v&agrave; server lu&ocirc;n nh&#7853;n d&#7919; li&#7879;u m&#7899;i theo th&#7901;i gian th&#7921;c (2 chi&#7873;u: server &#273;&#7871;n client ho&#7863;c client &#273;&#7871;n server). L&uacute;c n&agrave;y tr&ecirc;n server s&#7869; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n 1 v&ograve;ng l&#7863;p (loop) s&#7921; ki&#7879;n (b&#432;&#7899;c 1 &#273;&#7871;n 3) &#273;&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n l&#7841;i nhi&#7873;u l&#7847;n quy tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y v&agrave; b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; k&#7871;t n&#7889;i &#273;&#7871;n server t&#7915; 1 t&ecirc;n mi&#7873;n (domain) kh&aacute;c. Ngo&agrave;i ra b&#7841;n c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng websocket server c&#7911;a b&ecirc;n th&#7913; 3 cung c&#7845;p (v&iacute; d&#7909;: <a href="http://pusher.com/" target="_blank">http://pusher.com/</a>) v&agrave; vi&#7879;c c&ograve;n l&#7841;i l&agrave; b&#7841;n ch&#7881; vi&#7879;c code tr&ecirc;n client ( d&#7877; d&agrave;ng h&#417;n nhi&#7873;u v&igrave; tr&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&oacute; b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i code c&#7843; ph&iacute;a server v&agrave; client).</p>
<p>&#272;&#7875; d&#7877; hi&#7875;u h&#417;n, m&igrave;nh xin gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch th&ecirc;m c&aacute;i h&igrave;nh &#7903; tr&ecirc;n, h&igrave;nh n&agrave;y minh h&#7885;a nhi&#7873;u tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&oacute; th&#7875; x&#7843;y ra khi &aacute;p d&#7909;ng web socket:</p>
<ul><li>Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p 1: t&#7841;o connect v&#7899;i server ~&gt; nh&#7853;n 2 response t&#7915; server.</li>
<li>Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p 2: t&#7841;o connect v&#7899;i server ~&gt; nh&#7853;n 1 response t&#7915; server ~&gt; client g&#7917;i ti&#7871;p 1 request kh&aacute;c &#273;&#7871;n server.</li>
<li>Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p 3: t&#7841;o connect v&#7899;i server ~&gt; nh&#7853;n 2 response t&#7915; server ~&gt; server tr&#7843; v&#7873; ti&#7871;p 1 reponse kh&aacute;c cho client (m&#7863;c d&ugrave; kh&ocirc;ng&nbsp;c&oacute; request m&#7899;i n&agrave;o).</li>
</ul><h2>Comet:</h2>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-11344" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-comet.gif" alt="ky-thuat-lap-trinh-web-regular-http-13122015-comet" width="304" height="322"></p>
<p>Comet l&agrave; m&#7897;t thu&#7853;t ng&#7919; chung m&ocirc; t&#7843; vi&#7879;c server g&#7917;i response d&#7919; li&#7879;u cho client m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n 1 request r&otilde; r&agrave;ng. Ngo&agrave;i ra n&oacute; c&ograve;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c bi&#7871;t &#273;&#7871;n v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;i t&ecirc;n kh&aacute;c nh&#432;: Ajax push, Reverse Ajax, Two-way-web, HTTP Streaming, HTTP server push. Tr&ecirc;n th&#7921;c t&#7871; &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng comet c&oacute; th&#7875; d&ugrave;ng 1 trong 2 k&#7929; thu&#7853;t &#273;&oacute; l&agrave;: Streaming ho&#7863;c Long-Polling.</p>
<p>Comet c&oacute; m&#7897;t s&#7921; &#432;u vi&#7879;t &#273;&oacute; l&agrave; request t&#7915; client &#273;&#7871;n server c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c gi&#7919; trong 1 th&#7901;i gian d&agrave;i ( &#273;&#7871;n khi &#273;&#7841;t gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n time-out ) &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7907;i response t&#7915; server tr&#7843; v&#7873; ( xem h&igrave;nh m&ocirc; t&#7843; &#7903; tr&ecirc;n ), v&agrave; sau &#273;&oacute; s&#7869; ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c g&#7917;i request m&#7899;i &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7907;i response kh&aacute;c t&#7915; server.</p>
<p>M&#7897;t &#432;u &#273;i&#7875;m l&#7899;n n&#7919;a c&#7911;a Comet &#273;&oacute; l&agrave; lu&ocirc;n c&oacute; m&#7897;t li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t giao ti&#7871;p gi&#7919;a client v&agrave; server, server c&oacute; th&#7875; g&#7917;i response ngay khi request &#273;&#432;&#7907;c g&#7917;i &#273;&#7871;n ho&#7863;c t&iacute;ch l&#361;y response &#273;&#7875; g&#7917;i 1 l&#7847;n. Nh&#432;ng v&igrave; c&aacute;c request t&#7891;n t&#7841;i trong m&#7897;t th&#7901;i gian d&agrave;i ( long-lived request ) n&ecirc;n &#7903; server c&#7847;n m&#7897;t c&#417; ch&#7871; &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t &#273;&#7875; x&#7917; l&yacute; t&#7845;t c&#7843; request lo&#7841;i n&agrave;y.</p>
<p>K&#7929; thu&#7853;t Long-Polling m&igrave;nh &#273;&atilde; gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u &#7903; tr&ecirc;n r&#7891;i n&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7855;c l&#7841;i n&#7919;a, c&ograve;n v&#7899;i streaming b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; hi&#7875;u &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n th&#7871; n&agrave;y: h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c n&oacute; gi&#7889;ng v&#7899;i k&#7929; thu&#7853;t long-polling nh&#432;ng kh&aacute;c l&agrave; ta ch&#7881; kh&#7903;i t&#7841;o k&#7871;t n&#7889;i &#273;&#7871;n server m&#7897;t l&#7847;n v&agrave; g&#7917;i nh&#7853;n d&#7919; li&#7879;u th&ocirc;ng qua k&#7871;t n&#7889;i n&agrave;y ch&#7913; kh&ocirc;ng t&#7841;o k&#7871;t n&#7889;i m&#7899;i. ( k&#7929; thu&#7853;t streaming tr&ecirc;n th&#7921;c t&#7871; c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m web xem phim tr&#7921;c truy&#7871;n, t&#7843;i t&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;u coi t&#7899;i &#273;&oacute; v&agrave; ch&#7881; request &#273;&#7871;n file phim &#273;&uacute;ng 1 l&#7847;n).</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em>Techtalk via <a href="https://techmaster.vn/posts/33693/ky-thuat-long-polling-websockets-server-sent-events-comet">Techmaster</a></em></span></p></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";s:7:"Hieu Le";s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";N;}s:4:"date";s:19:"2016-11-06 12:00:23";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}}i:4;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:65:"Tại sao các ứng dụng lớn vẫn chưa chuyển qua Swift?";s:4:"link";s:74:"http://techtalk.vn/tai-sao-cac-ung-dung-lon-van-chua-chuyen-qua-swift.html";s:11:"description";s:603:"<div>T&ocirc;i lu&ocirc;n tin r&#7857;ng Swift l&agrave; t&#432;&#417;ng lai c&#7911;a l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh iOS. V&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; ch&#7881; l&agrave; th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m v&agrave; nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n c&#7843;n tr&#7903; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n ch&oacute;ng m&#7863;t c&#7911;a Swift. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng nh&#7887; th&igrave; Swift l&agrave; ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; l&yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng, nh&#432;ng v&#7899;i &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng l&#7899;n, s&#7869; t&#7889;n &iacute;t nh&#7845;t [&hellip;]</div>";s:7:"content";s:17114:"<div><p>T&ocirc;i lu&ocirc;n tin r&#7857;ng Swift l&agrave; t&#432;&#417;ng lai c&#7911;a <a href="http://ide.academy/cac-khoa-hoc/khoa-lap-trinh-ios-lam-15-ung-dung-thuc-te/">l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh iOS</a>. V&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; ch&#7881; l&agrave; <em>th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m</em> v&agrave; nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n c&#7843;n tr&#7903; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n ch&oacute;ng m&#7863;t c&#7911;a Swift. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng nh&#7887; th&igrave; Swift l&agrave; ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; l&yacute; t&#432;&#7903;ng, nh&#432;ng v&#7899;i &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng l&#7899;n, s&#7869; t&#7889;n &iacute;t nh&#7845;t 1 n&#259;m n&#7919;a &#273;&#7875; Swift th&#7875; hi&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c vai tr&ograve; c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh.</p>
<p>T&#7915; &ldquo;&#7913;ng d&#7909;ng l&#7899;n&rdquo; m&agrave; t&ocirc;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#7903; &#273;&acirc;y d&agrave;nh cho nh&#7919;ng h&#7841;ng m&#7909;c kh&aacute;c nhau, t&#7915; c&aacute;c d&ograve;ng code, &#273;&#7871;n s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n, m&#7913;c &#273;&#7897; ph&#7913;c t&#7841;p c&#7911;a &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng ho&#7863;c kh&#7843; n&#259;ng ch&#7883;u &#273;&#7921;ng th&#7845;p tr&#432;&#7899;c c&aacute;c v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873;. &#272;&#7847;u n&#259;m nay, chuy&ecirc;n gia Ryan Olson, sau khi ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch bi&#7875;u &#273;&#7891; Top 100 apps mi&#7877;n ph&iacute; tr&ecirc;n App Store, ch&#7881; ra r&#7857;ng 89% &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng kh&ocirc;ng d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#7871;n Swift. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#7891;ng ngh&#297;a l&agrave; ch&#7881; c&oacute; 11% c&ograve;n l&#7841;i &#273;&atilde; ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n Swift. M&#7897;t &#273;&#7897;i ng&#361; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng m&agrave; t&ocirc;i t&#7915;ng n&oacute;i chuy&#7879;n c&#361;ng &#273;&atilde; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u th&#7917; nghi&#7879;m v&#7899;i Swift nh&#432;ng ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; m&#7863;c &#273;&#7883;nh trong h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c c&#7911;a h&#7885; v&#7851;n l&agrave; Objective-C.</p>
<p>N&#7871;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh <a href="http://ide.academy/cac-khoa-hoc/khoa-lap-trinh-ios-lam-15-ung-dung-thuc-te/">1 &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng</a> nh&#7887; th&igrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; ng&#432;ng &#273;&#7885;c t&#7841;i &#273;&acirc;y v&igrave; &#432;u &#273;i&#7875;m c&#7911;a Swift 3.0 v&#7851;n v&#432;&#7907;t tr&#7897;i h&#417;n nh&#7919;ng nguy c&#417; m&agrave; n&oacute; g&acirc;y ra. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, n&#7871;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang t&ograve; m&ograve; v&#7873; nh&#7919;ng th&aacute;ch th&#7913;c c&#7911;a c&aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p l&#7899;n, c&aacute;c codebases l&#7899;n v&agrave; c&aacute;c dependencies ph&#7913;c t&#7841;p th&igrave; b&agrave;i vi&#7871;t n&agrave;y s&#7869; gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch l&yacute; do t&#7841;i sao c&aacute;c d&#7921; &aacute;n v&#7851;n c&ograve;n &#273;ang ng&#7853;p ng&#7915;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n Swift.</p>
<h3><strong>Language Churn</strong></h3>
<p>M&#7895;i c&#7853;p nh&#7853;t c&#7911;a Xcode l&#7841;i d&#7851;n &#273;&#7871;n nh&#7919;ng thay &#273;&#7893;i v&#7873; ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; v&agrave; ph&aacute; &#273;i c&aacute;c d&ograve;ng code. Th&#7881;nh tho&#7843;ng b&#7841;n &#273;&#7875; code migrator l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, th&#7881;nh tho&#7843;ng b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i ch&#7881;nh s&#7917;a th&#7911; c&ocirc;ng. B&#7841;n ch&#7881; c&oacute; th&#7875; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c vi&#7879;c n&agrave;y n&#7871;u c&oacute; d&#432;&#7899;i 30.000 d&ograve;ng codes, nh&#432;ng h&#7847;u h&#7871;t c&aacute;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng tr&ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i l&#7841;i kh&ocirc;ng nh&#432; th&#7871;. Ch&#7859;ng h&#7841;n, &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng Facebook c&oacute; 18.000 classes, t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#432;&#417;ng v&#7899;i h&agrave;ng tri&#7879;u d&ograve;ng code.</p>
<p><a href="http://ide.academy/cac-khoa-hoc/khoa-lap-trinh-ios-lam-15-ung-dung-thuc-te/"><img class="aligncenter" src="https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v3/yb/r/nrpLiSINthw.png" alt="K&#7871;t qu&#7843; h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh cho facebook"></a></p>
<p>N&#7871;u 2% c&#7911;a codebase chuy&#7875;n sang Swift s&#7869; l&agrave; 20.000 d&ograve;ng codes. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng &#7903; 1 n&#417;i m&agrave; s&#7869; t&#7843;n ra trong c&aacute;c experiments&nbsp;&#273;&atilde; b&#7883; v&ocirc; hi&#7879;u ho&#7863;c c&aacute;c refactored code c&#361; v&#7851;n c&ograve;n &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng.</p>
<p>&#272;&#7897;i ng&#361; k&#297; s&#432; ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m migration s&#7869; m&#7845;t 1 tu&#7847;n theo d&otilde;i c&aacute;c t&aacute;c gi&#7843; g&#7889;c, x&aacute;c th&#7921;c code &#273;&atilde; c&#7853;p nh&#7853;t v&#7851;n ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng theo &#273;&uacute;ng k&#7871; ho&#7841;ch.</p>
<p>D&#297; nhi&ecirc;n, c&ocirc;ng ty kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; ng&#7915;ng l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh migration. M&#7895;i ng&agrave;y l&#7841;i c&oacute; code m&#7899;i ra &#273;&#7901;i v&agrave; xung &#273;&#7897;t c&#7913; th&#7871; t&#259;ng l&ecirc;n.</p>
<h3><strong>ABI b&#7845;t &#7893;n</strong></h3>
<p>V&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; kh&aacute;c, &iacute;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c bi&#7871;t &#273;&#7871;n l&agrave; s&#7921; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n b&ecirc;n trong c&#7911;a Swift &ndash; quan tr&#7885;ng nh&#7845;t l&agrave; Application Binary Interface. M&#7897;t ABI s&#7869; nh&#7853;n di&#7879;n layout c&#7911;a c&aacute;c c&#7845;u tr&uacute;c d&#7919; li&#7879;u, c&aacute;ch c&aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i s&#7889; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7849;y l&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n stack, c&aacute;ch c&aacute;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng t&#7841;o n&ecirc;n c&aacute;c calls h&#7879; th&#7889;ng v&agrave; nh&#7919;ng chi ti&#7871;t kh&aacute;c 99,99% kh&ocirc;ng li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh h&#7857;ng ng&agrave;y.</p>
<p>Swift 3.0 &#273;&atilde; d&#7921; &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7869; kh&oacute;a ABI l&#7841;i, nh&#432;ng &#273;&#7897;i ng&#361; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh Swift &#273;&atilde; th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o g&#7847;n &#273;&acirc;y l&agrave; h&#7885; s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;m v&#7853;y n&#7919;a. &#272;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y &#273;&#7891;ng ngh&#297;a v&#7899;i &#273;i&#7873;u g&igrave;?</p>
<p>M&#7897;t ABI g&#7863;p v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; khi 2 modules code t&aacute;ch bi&#7879;t c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i &ldquo;n&oacute;i chuy&#7879;n&rdquo; v&#7899;i nhau. V&iacute; d&#7909;, C c&oacute; th&#7875; g&#7885;i code Ruby mi&#7877;n l&agrave; n&oacute; thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p 1 frame stack theo d&#7921; &#273;o&aacute;n c&#7911;a runtime.</p>
<p>Gi&#7843; nh&#432; b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh 1 framework v&#7899;i Swift 2.2 v&agrave; &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng c&#361;ng ch&#7841;y tr&ecirc;n Swift 2.2. D&ugrave; c&#7843; 2 apps &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#273;&#7897;c l&#7853;p, ch&uacute;ng v&#7851;n n&oacute;i chuy&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c v&#7899;i nhau, v&igrave; ch&uacute;ng &#273;&#7873;u c&oacute; th&#7875; n&oacute;i trong c&#7845;u tr&uacute;c &#7903; m&#7913;c &#273;&#7897; th&#7845;p.</p>
<p>Gi&#7843; nh&#432; b&#7841;n<a href="http://ide.academy/cac-khoa-hoc/khoa-lap-trinh-ios-lam-15-ung-dung-thuc-te/"> chuy&#7875;n app sang Swift 3.0</a>. N&#7871;u ABI thay &#273;&#7893;i &#273;&#7875; c&aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i s&#7889; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t &#7903; c&aacute;c v&#7883; tr&iacute; kh&aacute;c nhau trong stack frame th&igrave; nhi&#7873;u kh&#7843; n&#259;ng b&#7841;n s&#7869; b&#7883; crash. C&aacute;ch gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t duy nh&#7845;t l&agrave; compile m&#7885;i th&#7913; trong c&ugrave;ng 1 phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n Swift. T&iacute;ch h&#7907;p framework v&agrave;o Swift 3.0 c&ugrave;ng th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m v&#7899;i &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng ch&iacute;nh.</p>
<h3><strong>Kh&ocirc;ng x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng 1 SDK trong Swift</strong></h3>
<p>N&#7871;u b&#7841;n &#273;ang x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng 1 pre-compiled SDK, ABI kh&ocirc;ng &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh s&#7869; khi&#7871;n m&#7885;i th&#7913; tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh th&#7843;m h&#7885;a. Khi phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n m&#7899;i c&#7911;a Swift &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&ocirc;ng b&#7889;, b&#7841;n c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i recompile ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c v&agrave; ra m&#7855;t ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n m&#7899;i nh&#7845;t.</p>
<p>Phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n m&#7899;i nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a SDK l&agrave; 2.0. C&aacute;c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; v&#7851;n &#273;ang ch&#7841;y tr&ecirc;n 1.0 v&igrave; phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n 2.0 c&oacute; nh&#7919;ng thay &#273;&#7893;i r&#7845;t l&#7899;n. B&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; ph&#7843;i t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n m&#7899;i nh&#7845;t c&#7911;a SDK v&agrave;o<a href="http://ide.academy/cac-khoa-hoc/khoa-lap-trinh-ios-lam-15-ung-dung-thuc-te/"> Swift m&#7899;i nh&#7845;t</a> v&agrave; b&#7841;n c&#361;ng ph&#7843;i t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p SDK c&#361; n&#7919;a.</p>
<p>M&#7897;t v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; kh&aacute;c c&oacute; th&#7875; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n kh&#7843; n&#259;ng ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n SDK l&agrave; dung l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7843;i xu&#7889;ng cao. V&igrave; c&aacute;c th&#432; vi&#7879;n Swift ch&iacute;nh kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chia s&#7867; tr&ecirc;n iOS, n&ecirc;n c&aacute;c th&#432; vi&#7879;n n&agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p trong &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng. Trong 1 &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng thu&#7847;n Objective-C, th&ecirc;m 1 SDK ch&#7841;y Swift s&#7869; t&#7889;n &#273;&#7871;n 5 MB.</p>
<p><a href="http://ide.academy/cac-khoa-hoc/khoa-lap-trinh-ios-lam-15-ung-dung-thuc-te/"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://images.techhive.com/images/article/2014/10/swift-logo-100468480-primary.idge.jpg" alt="K&#7871;t qu&#7843; h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh cho tooling in swift language"></a></p>
<h3><strong>&#272;&#7875; m&#7855;t &#273;&#7871;n c&aacute;c dependencies ph&#7913;c t&#7841;p</strong></h3>
<p>C&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty v&#7899;i nhi&#7873;u &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng chia s&#7867; chung c&aacute;c frameworks n&#7897;i b&#7897;. Nh&#7919;ng frameworks n&agrave;y c&oacute; th&#7875; g&#7891;m c&#7845;u tr&uacute;c nh&#432; networking stack ho&#7863;c c&aacute;c t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng thi&ecirc;n v&#7873; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m nh&#432; m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh &#273;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p.</p>
<p>B&#7903;i v&igrave; t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c frameworks c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i ch&#7841;y c&ugrave;ng 1 phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n Swift, n&ecirc;n t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng c&#7847;n chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i c&ugrave;ng 1 l&uacute;c. M&#7897;t c&ocirc;ng ty nh&#432; Facebook c&#7847;n t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng Facebook, Messenger, Groups v&agrave; t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng th&#7913; kh&aacute;c. Vi&#7879;c n&agrave;y &#273;&#7891;ng ngh&#297;a v&#7899;i vi&#7879;c ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p h&agrave;ng t&aacute; &#273;&#7897;i ng&#361; v&agrave; h&agrave;ng tr&#259;m l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n.</p>
<h3><strong>C&aacute;c v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; v&#7899;i Tooling</strong></h3>
<p>D&ugrave; cho c&aacute;c frameworks &#273;&#432;&#7907;c compile trong c&ugrave;ng 1 v&ugrave;ng l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c, LLDB v&#7851;n c&oacute; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; v&#7899;i c&aacute;c frameworks ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; h&#7895;n h&#7907;p. V&iacute; d&#7909;, b&#7841;n s&#7869; b&#7883; crash n&#7871;u b&#7841;n thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p breakpoint trong network stack (Framework A) s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7889;i s&#7889; l&agrave; model c&#7911;a b&#7841;n (Framework B).</p>
<p>Trong c&aacute;c codebases l&#7899;n, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng frameworks do ch&iacute;nh b&#7841;n code &#273;&#432;&#7907;c compile tr&#432;&#7899;c s&#7869; gi&uacute;p gi&#7843;m &#273;&aacute;ng k&#7875; th&#7901;i gian l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh. &#272;&aacute;ng ti&#7871;c l&agrave;, b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i hy sinh kh&#7843; n&#259;ng debug, &#273;&#7893;i l&#7845;y th&#7901;i gian l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh l&acirc;u h&#417;n ho&#7863;c khi b&#7841;n &#273;&#7871;n th&#7901;i k&igrave; debug, s&#7869; g&#7863;p ph&#7843;i nh&#7919;ng m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u projects b&#7845;p b&ecirc;nh tr&ecirc;n c&#417; s&#7903; t&#7915;ng file m&#7897;t.</p>
<p>Khi ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p Objective-C v&agrave; <a href="http://ide.academy/cac-khoa-hoc/khoa-lap-trinh-ios-lam-15-ung-dung-thuc-te/">Swift</a> qua nhi&#7873;u frameworks, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; khi&#7871;n SourceKit b&#7883; crash nh&#432; t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng x&#7843;y ra v&agrave;o 7/2014 v&#7899;i Swift 1.0. B&#7841;n s&#7869; m&#7845;t syntax highlighting v&agrave; c&aacute;c &#273;o&#7841;n code ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n. &#272;&acirc;y l&agrave; r&agrave;o c&#7843;n l&#7899;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n Swift ho&#7863;c khi dev l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c v&#7899;i c&aacute;c t&ecirc;n method d&agrave;i b&#7845;t t&#7853;n c&#7911;a Cocoa.</p>
<p><a href="http://ide.academy/cac-khoa-hoc/khoa-lap-trinh-ios-lam-15-ung-dung-thuc-te/"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://www.jpsim.com/images/posts/sidekick.jpg" alt="K&#7871;t qu&#7843; h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh cho tooling issue in swift language"></a></p>
<p>Tuy &#273;i&#7873;u n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng li&ecirc;n quan nhi&#7873;u &#273;&#7871;n ABI, nh&#432;ng t&iacute;nh &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a ABI v&#7851;n l&agrave; 1 r&agrave;o c&#7843;n.</p>
<h3><strong>Kh&#7843; n&#259;ng t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p h&#7895; tr&#7907; framework</strong></h3>
<p>&#272;&#7875; g&oacute;i g&#7885;n ph&#7847;n di&#7877;n gi&#7843;i v&#7873; ABI, t&ocirc;i s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; t&#7853;p trung v&agrave;o nh&#7919;ng &#273;i&#7875;m b&#7845;t l&#7907;i. ABI &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u c&aacute;c r&agrave;o c&#7843;n v&agrave; t&igrave;nh tr&#7841;ng language churn.</p>
<p>M&#7897;t chi&#7871;n l&#432;&#7907;c m&agrave; t&ocirc;i t&#7915;ng th&#7845;y &#7903; c&aacute;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng l&#7899;n l&agrave; d&ugrave; code kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng trong b&#7845;t k&igrave; &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c, ph&acirc;n gi&#7843;i &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng th&agrave;nh c&aacute;c frameworks. Frameworks h&#7895; tr&#7907; testing d&#7877; d&agrave;ng h&#417;n v&agrave; l&agrave;m r&otilde; quy&#7873;n s&#7903; h&#7919;u code.</p>
<p>V&#7899;i 1 ABI &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; gi&#7919; c&aacute;c frameworks n&agrave;y &#7903; phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n Swift c&#361; v&agrave; t&iacute;ch h&#7907;p ch&uacute;ng t&#7915;ng b&#432;&#7899;c m&#7897;t. M&#7895;i &#273;&#7897;i ng&#361; s&#7869; ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i code c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh.</p>
<h3><strong>K&#7871;t</strong></h3>
<p>B&agrave;i vi&#7871;t n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7875; b&ecirc;u x&#7845;u &#273;&#7897;i ng&#361; Swift. &#272;&#7897;i ng&#361; Swift &#273;&atilde; &#432;u ti&ecirc;n ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; v&agrave; h&#7879; sinh th&aacute;i, thay v&igrave; t&#7853;p trung v&agrave;o t&iacute;nh &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t c&aacute;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p nh&#7887; nh&#7863;t. &#272;&oacute; l&agrave; s&#7921; tr&#7843; gi&aacute; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n h&#7907;p l&yacute;.</p>
<p>M&#7863;c d&ugrave; platform &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh, c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng ty l&#7899;n chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i platforms v&#7899;i t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897; r&#7845;t ch&#7853;m. Adobe t&#7889;n 1 th&#7853;p k&#7881; &#273;&#7875; chuy&#7875;n t&#7915; Photoshop t&#7915; Carbon sang Cocoa. Thay v&igrave; nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u nh&#7919;ng &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng l&#7899;n, b&#7841;n s&#7869; c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7919;ng l&#7901;i khuy&ecirc;n t&#7889;t t&#7915; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i chuy&#7875;n &#273;&#7893;i s&#7899;m h&#417;n v&agrave; s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng b&#7883; r&agrave;ng bu&#7897;c b&#7903;i cam k&#7871;t nhi&#7873;u n&#259;m v&#7899;i t&iacute;nh n&#259;ng &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh.</p>
<p>&#272;i&#7873;u quan tr&#7885;ng n&#7919;a t&ocirc;i mu&#7889;n nh&#7855;c l&#7841;i l&agrave;: h&#7847;u h&#7871;t nh&#7919;ng &#273;i&#7873;u t&ocirc;i &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7873; c&#7853;p c&oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng kh&ocirc;ng ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. C&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7841;n &#273;ang l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c v&#7899;i 1 codebase nh&#7887; h&#417;n, c&aacute;c dependencies &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n h&#417;n. N&ecirc;n nh&#7899;, l&#7907;i &iacute;ch Swift 3.0 mang &#273;&#7871;n lu&ocirc;n l&#7899;n nh&#7919;ng &#273;i&#7875;m b&#7845;t l&#7907;i.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Ngu&#7891;n: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/idevietnam">IDE Academy</a>&nbsp;via <a href="https://medium.com/@sandofsky/why-big-apps-arent-moving-to-swift-yet-f8e9a89ef661#.trxqy8v11">Medium</a></strong></p></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";s:7:"Ai Hien";s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";N;}s:4:"date";s:19:"2016-11-06 08:00:59";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}}i:5;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:58:"10 lỗi các dev NodeJS thường mắc phải (phần 3)";s:4:"link";s:68:"http://techtalk.vn/10-loi-cac-dev-nodejs-thuong-mac-phai-phan-3.html";s:11:"description";s:515:"<div>PH&#7846;N 1 &ndash; PH&#7846;N 2 L&#7895;i&nbsp;#8: B&#7887; qua nh&#7919;ng l&#7907;i &#273;i&#7875;m c&#7911;a APIs streaming Gi&#7843; s&#7917; b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng 1 web server nh&#432; proxy nh&#7887;, ph&#7843;n h&#7891;i c&aacute;c requests b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch l&#7845;y content t&#7915; 1 web server kh&aacute;c. Nh&#432; v&iacute; d&#7909; b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i, ch&uacute;ng ta ph&#7843;i x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng 1 web server hi&#7875;n th&#7883; c&aacute;c [&hellip;]</div>";s:7:"content";s:10552:"<div><h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="http://ide.academy/featured/10-loi-thuong-ma-cac-dev-nodejs-thuong-mac-phai-phan-1/">PH&#7846;N 1</a> &ndash; <a href="http://ide.academy/featured/10-loi-thuong-ma-cac-dev-nodejs-thuong-mac-phai-phan-2/">PH&#7846;N 2</a></strong></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: left;"><strong>L&#7895;i&nbsp;#8: B&#7887; qua nh&#7919;ng l&#7907;i &#273;i&#7875;m c&#7911;a APIs streaming</strong></h3>
<p>Gi&#7843; s&#7917; b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng 1 web server nh&#432; proxy nh&#7887;, ph&#7843;n h&#7891;i c&aacute;c requests b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch l&#7845;y content t&#7915; 1 web server kh&aacute;c. Nh&#432; v&iacute; d&#7909; b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i, ch&uacute;ng ta ph&#7843;i x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng 1 web server hi&#7875;n th&#7883; c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh Gravatar:</p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">var http = require('http')
var crypto = require('crypto')

http.createServer()
.on('request', function(req, res) {
	var email = req.url.substr(req.url.lastIndexOf('/')+1)
	if(!email) {
		res.writeHead(404)
		return res.end()
	}

	var buf = new Buffer(1024*1024)
	http.get('http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/'+crypto.createHash('md5').update(email).digest('hex'), function(resp) {
		var size = 0
		resp.on('data', function(chunk) {
			chunk.copy(buf, size)
			size += chunk.length
		})
		.on('end', function() {
			res.write(buf.slice(0, size))
			res.end()
		})
	})
})
.listen(8080)</pre><p>Trong v&iacute; d&#7909; v&#7873; 1 v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; c&#7911;a Nodejs, ch&uacute;ng ta &#273;ang l&#7845;y h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh t&#7915; Gravatar, th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o 1 Buffer, sau &#273;&oacute; ph&#7843;n h&#7891;i l&#7841;i request. V&igrave; c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh Gravatar kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; l&#7899;n n&ecirc;n vi&#7879;c n&agrave;y c&#361;ng kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; t&#7879;. Nh&#432;ng, n&#7871;u k&iacute;ch c&#7905; c&#7911;a c&aacute;c contents m&agrave; ch&uacute;ng ta &#273;ang proxy l&agrave; h&agrave;ng ng&agrave;n Megabytes th&igrave; l&#7841;i l&agrave; chuy&#7879;n kh&aacute;c.</p>
<p>C&aacute;ch kh&aacute;c t&#7889;t h&#417;n s&#7869; nh&#432; sau:</p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">http.createServer()
.on('request', function(req, res) {
	var email = req.url.substr(req.url.lastIndexOf('/')+1)
	if(!email) {
		res.writeHead(404)
		return res.end()
	}

	http.get('http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/'+crypto.createHash('md5').update(email).digest('hex'), function(resp) {
		resp.pipe(res)
	})
})
.listen(8080)</pre><p>&#7902; &#273;&acirc;y, ch&uacute;ng ta l&#7845;y h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh v&agrave; tr&#7843; ph&#7843;n h&#7891;i l&#7841;i cho client, m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n &#273;&#7885;c to&agrave;n b&#7897; content trong buffer tr&#432;&#7899;c khi th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n n&oacute;.</p>
<h3 id="mistake-9-using-consolelog-for-debugging-purposes"><strong>L&#7895;i&nbsp;#9: S&#7917; d&#7909;ng Console.log v&#7899;i m&#7909;c &#273;&iacute;ch debug</strong></h3>
<p>Trong Node.js, &ldquo;console.log&rdquo; cho ph&eacute;p b&#7841;n print h&#7847;u h&#7871;t m&#7885;i th&#7913; trong console (giao di&#7879;n &#273;i&#7873;u khi&#7875;n). Chuy&#7875;n 1 &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng v&agrave;o &#273;&oacute; v&agrave; n&oacute; s&#7869; print th&agrave;nh&nbsp;1 &#273;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng Javascript b&#7857;ng ch&#7919;. N&oacute; ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n c&aacute;c &#273;&#7889;i s&#7889; ng&#7851;u nhi&ecirc;n b&#7845;t k&igrave; v&agrave; print ch&uacute;ng t&#7841;i c&aacute;c v&ugrave;ng t&aacute;ch bi&#7879;t. C&oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u l&yacute; do t&#7841;i sao 1 l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n c&#7843;m th&#7845;y b&#7883; c&aacute;m d&#7895; ph&#7843;i s&#7917; d&#7909;ng console.org &#273;&#7875; debug code c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh, nh&#432;ng t&ocirc;i khuy&#7871;n kh&iacute;ch b&#7841;n n&ecirc;n tr&aacute;nh d&ugrave;ng &ldquo;console.org&rdquo; trong code th&#7853;t. B&#7841;n kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n vi&#7871;t &ldquo;console.log&rdquo; xuy&ecirc;n su&#7889;t c&aacute;c code c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh &#273;&#7875; debug v&agrave; sau &#273;&oacute; x&oacute;a ch&uacute;ng khi kh&ocirc;ng c&#7847;n n&#7919;a. Thay v&agrave;o &#273;&oacute;, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng 1 trong nh&#7919;ng libraries hay &#273;&#432;&#7907;c x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m ri&ecirc;ng vi&#7879;c n&agrave;y, nh&#432;&nbsp;<a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/debug" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">debug</a>.</p>
<p>C&aacute;c packages nh&#432; tr&ecirc;n s&#7869; l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng c&aacute;ch ti&#7879;n l&#7907;i &#273;&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t v&agrave; v&ocirc; hi&#7879;u v&agrave;i d&ograve;ng debug n&agrave;o &#273;&oacute; khi b&#7841;n b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng. V&iacute; d&#7909;, v&#7899;i debug, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p m&ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng DEBUG bi&#7871;n th&#7875; &#273;&#7875; ng&#259;n d&ograve;ng debut b&#7845;t k&igrave;&nbsp;kh&ocirc;ng b&#7883; print &#273;&#7871;n terminal.</p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">// app.js
var debug = require(&lsquo;debug&rsquo;)(&lsquo;app&rsquo;)
debug(&rsquo;Hello, %s!&rsquo;, &lsquo;world&rsquo;)</pre><p>&#272;&#7875; k&iacute;ch ho&#7841;t c&aacute;c debug lines, ch&#7881; c&#7847;n ch&#7841;y code n&agrave;y v&#7899;i m&ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng DEBUG bi&#7871;n th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p v&#7899;i &ldquo;app&rdquo; ho&#7863;c &ldquo;*&rdquo;:</p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">DEBUG=app node app.js</pre><p></p>
<h3 id="mistake-10-not-using-supervisor-programs"><strong>L&#7895;i&nbsp;#10: Kh&ocirc;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&aacute;c ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh&nbsp;supervisor</strong></h3>
<p>B&#7845;t k&#7875; code Node.js c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;ang ch&#7841;y trong production ho&#7863;c trong m&ocirc;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh n&#7897;i b&#7897;, th&igrave; 1 ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh supervisor qu&#7843;n l&yacute; code l&agrave; c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; h&#7919;u &iacute;ch &#273;&#7875; t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, d&agrave;n x&#7871;p ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. M&#7897;t practice th&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&aacute;c developers khuy&#7871;n d&ugrave;ng &#273;&#7875; thi&#7871;t k&#7871; v&agrave; ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n c&aacute;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i s&#7869; cho th&#7845;y code c&#7911;a b&#7841;n ph&#7843;i th&#7845;t b&#7841;i s&#7899;m. N&#7871;u m&#7897;t l&#7895;i b&#7845;t ng&#7901; x&#7843;y ra, &#273;&#7915;ng c&#7889; g&#7855;ng gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t n&oacute;, h&atilde;y &#273;&#7875; ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n crash v&agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng supervisor &#273;&#7875; kh&#7903;i &#273;&#7897;ng l&#7841;i trong v&agrave;i gi&acirc;y.</p>
<p>L&#7907;i &iacute;ch c&#7911;a c&aacute;c ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh supervisor kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; l&agrave; vi&#7879;c kh&#7903;i &#273;&#7897;ng l&#7841;i c&aacute;c ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh b&#7883; crash. Nh&#7919;ng c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; n&agrave;y cho ph&eacute;p b&#7841;n kh&#7903;i &#273;&#7897;ng ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh l&uacute;c crash, c&#361;ng nh&#432; kh&#7903;i &#273;&#7897;ng l&#7841;i ch&uacute;ng khi 1 s&#7889; files thay &#273;&#7893;i. Nh&#7901; &#273;&oacute;, c&aacute;c&nbsp;ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh Node.js &#273;em &#273;&#7871;n tr&#7843;i nghi&#7879;m t&#7889;t h&#417;n.</p>
<p>Hi&#7879;n nay c&oacute; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh supervisor d&agrave;nh cho Node.js nh&#432;</p>
<ul><li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/packages/pm2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">pm2</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/packages/forever" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">forever</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/packages/nodemon" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">nodemon</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/packages/supervisor" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">supervisor</a></li>
</ul><p>T&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; n&agrave;y &#273;&#7873;u c&oacute; &#273;i&#7875;m t&#7889;t v&agrave; &#273;i&#7875;m kh&ocirc;ng t&#7889;t. M&#7897;t s&#7889; c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7875; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; nhi&#7873;u &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng trong c&ugrave;ng 1 thi&#7871;t b&#7883;, trong khi c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; kh&aacute;c h&#7895; tr&#7907; qu&#7843;n l&yacute; log t&#7889;t h&#417;n. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, n&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u v&#7899;i 1 ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh nh&#432; th&#7871;, t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; &#273;&#7873;u &#7893;n.</p>
<h3 id="conclusion"><strong>K&#7871;t</strong></h3>
<p>M&#7897;t v&agrave;i v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; c&#7911;a&nbsp;Node.js c&oacute; th&#7875; s&#7869; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng t&#7891;i t&#7879; &#273;&#7871;n ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. M&#7897;t s&#7889; l&agrave; nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n khi&#7871;n b&#7841;n b&#7921;c m&igrave;nh khi b&#7841;n &#273;ang c&#7889; g&#7855;ng ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n nh&#7919;ng th&#7913; &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n nh&#7845;t trong Node.js. M&#7863;c d&ugrave; Node.js &#273;&atilde; h&#7895; tr&#7907; r&#7845;t nhi&#7873;u cho nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i m&#7899;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u, nh&#7919;ng v&#7851;n c&oacute; v&agrave;i ch&#7895; b&#7883; r&#7889;i. C&aacute;c l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh vi&ecirc;n t&#7915; c&aacute;c ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh kh&aacute;c c&oacute; th&#7875; g&#7863;p v&agrave;i v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; tr&ecirc;n&nbsp;ho&#7863;c m&#7897;t s&#7889; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n trong c&aacute;c developer&nbsp;<a href="https://www.toptal.com/nodejs/job-description">Node.js m&#7899;i</a>.</p>
<p>May m&#7855;n l&agrave;, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; d&#7877; d&agrave;ng tr&aacute;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c.</p>
<p>T&ocirc;i hy v&#7885;ng h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n ng&#7855;n n&agrave;y s&#7869; gi&uacute;p nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i m&#7899;i b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u vi&#7871;t code Node.js t&#7889;t h&#417;n v&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh v&agrave; ti&#7879;n &iacute;ch h&#417;n.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>Ngu&#7891;n: <a href="https://www.toptal.com/nodejs/top-10-common-nodejs-developer-mistakes">toptal.com</a> via <a href="https://www.facebook.com/idevietnam/">IDE Academy</a>&nbsp;l&#432;&#7907;c d&#7883;ch</strong></p></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Thien Bui";s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";N;}s:4:"date";s:19:"2016-11-06 01:00:00";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}}i:6;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:18:"Pro PHP and jQuery";s:4:"link";s:42:"http://techtalk.vn/pro-php-and-jquery.html";s:11:"description";s:45:"<div>T&#7843;i t&#7841;i &#273;&acirc;y</div>";s:7:"content";s:164:"<div><h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>T&#7843;i t&#7841;i <a href="http://slimshare.com/file/57f87f7a8c862b2e318b4567">&#273;&acirc;y</a></strong></h3></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Thien Bui";s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";N;}s:4:"date";s:19:"2016-11-05 13:00:17";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}}i:7;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:32:"Cái tôi cá nhân khi teamwork";s:4:"link";s:52:"http://techtalk.vn/cai-toi-ca-nhan-khi-teamwork.html";s:11:"description";s:591:"<div>Teamwork c&oacute; l&#7869; l&agrave; t&#7915; kh&oacute;a kh&aacute; quan tr&#7885;ng v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; thi&#7871;u trong c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c khi c&#7847;n gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t theo nh&oacute;m, s&#7889; &#273;&ocirc;ng. T&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch v&#7873; kh&aacute;i ni&#7879;m, nguy&ecirc;n t&#7855;c chung c&#7911;a n&oacute; v&igrave; n&oacute; kh&aacute; ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n. C&aacute;i t&ocirc;i mu&#7889;n n&oacute;i trong b&agrave;i vi&#7871;t n&agrave;y ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; kh&iacute;a c&#7841;nh c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i [&hellip;]</div>";s:7:"content";s:10074:"<div><p class="p1"><span class="s1">Teamwork c&oacute; l&#7869; l&agrave; t&#7915; kh&oacute;a kh&aacute; quan tr&#7885;ng v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; thi&#7871;u trong c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c khi c&#7847;n gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t theo nh&oacute;m, s&#7889; &#273;&ocirc;ng. T&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng gi&#7843;i th&iacute;ch v&#7873; kh&aacute;i ni&#7879;m, nguy&ecirc;n t&#7855;c chung c&#7911;a n&oacute; v&igrave; n&oacute; kh&aacute; ph&#7893; bi&#7871;n.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">C&aacute;i t&ocirc;i mu&#7889;n n&oacute;i trong b&agrave;i vi&#7871;t n&agrave;y ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; kh&iacute;a c&#7841;nh c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i c&aacute; nh&acirc;n trong teamwork. Li&#7879;u l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c teamwork ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; n&ecirc;n b&#7887; qua c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i c&aacute; nh&acirc;n?</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Tr&#432;&#7899;c ti&ecirc;n t&ocirc;i c&oacute; m&#7897;t v&iacute; d&#7909;:</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1"> M&#7897;t v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; h&oacute;c b&uacute;a X &#273;ang c&#7847;n t&igrave;m h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t, trong nh&oacute;m c&oacute;:</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&ndash; Anh A &#273;&#432;a ra gi&#7843;i ph&aacute;p AX v&agrave; tin r&#7857;ng v&#7899;i kinh nghi&#7879;m l&acirc;u n&#259;m c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh, anh ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n &#273;&uacute;ng.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&ndash; Anh B &#273;&#432;a ra gi&#7843;i ph&aacute;p BX v&agrave; tin r&#7857;ng v&#7899;i kh&#7843; n&#259;ng h&#7885;c h&#7887;i<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp; </span>nhanh c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh, c&#7897;ng v&#7899;i kh&#7843; n&#259;ng logic cao th&igrave; anh ta &#273;&uacute;ng.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&ndash; Anh C c&#361;ng c&oacute; gi&#7843;i ph&aacute;p CX c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh nh&#432;ng c&ograve;n l&uacute;ng t&uacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng d&aacute;m &#273;&#432;a ra &yacute; ki&#7871;n c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh v&igrave; s&#7907; sai.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>&ndash; Anh D th&igrave; ch&#432;a c&oacute; gi&#7843;i ph&aacute;p g&igrave; nh&#432;ng m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i ai n&oacute;i g&igrave; c&#361;ng g&#7853;t g&ugrave;!</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Anh A v&agrave; anh B tranh lu&#7853;n v&#7899;i nhau v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng anh n&agrave;o ch&#7883;u l&#7855;ng nghe anh n&agrave;o. C, D th&igrave; ng&#7891;i l&#7855;ng nghe A, B tranh lu&#7853;n m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng ho he g&igrave; v&igrave; A, B ai c&#361;ng c&oacute; l&yacute;.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-10066" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/1.jpeg" alt="1" width="640" height="480" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/1.jpeg 640w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/1-300x225.jpeg 300w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/1-80x60.jpeg 80w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/1-265x198.jpeg 265w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/1-560x420.jpeg 560w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px"></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">&#7902; v&iacute; d&#7909; tr&ecirc;n b&#7841;n th&#7845;y A, B, C, D &#273;&atilde; l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c teamwork t&#7889;t ch&#432;a? R&otilde; r&agrave;ng c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i c&aacute; nh&acirc;n trong tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p n&agrave;y &#273;&atilde; l&agrave;m ph&aacute; h&#7887;ng c&aacute;i m&#7909;c ti&ecirc;u cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng l&agrave; t&igrave;m h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873;.</span></p>
<ul class="ul1"><li class="li1"><span class="s1">A, B v&igrave; c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i c&aacute; nh&acirc;n q&uacute;a cao m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7883;u l&#7855;ng nghe &#273;&#7889;i ph&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#7875; t&igrave;m ra h&#432;&#7899;ng gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t chung &#7893;n th&#7887;a.</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">C th&igrave; &#273;&#7871;n c&oacute; gi&#7843;i ph&aacute;p m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng d&aacute;m n&oacute;i, th&igrave; c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i c&aacute; nh&acirc;n &#273;&#7875; &#273;&acirc;u.</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">D th&igrave; qu&aacute; trung l&#7853;p</span></li>
</ul><p class="p1"><span class="s1">&#272;&#7875; c&acirc;n b&#7857;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i c&aacute; nh&acirc;n khi l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c t&#7853;p th&#7875; t&ocirc;i tin r&#7857;ng kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7881; l&agrave; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; c&#7911;a m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i m&#7899;i &#273;i l&agrave;m m&agrave; c&ograve;n v&#7899;i ng&#432;&#7901;i c&oacute; kinh nghi&#7879;m l&acirc;u n&#259;m. Bi&#7871;t v&#7913;t &#273;i c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i c&aacute; nh&acirc;n trong th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m th&iacute;ch h&#7907;p &#273;&#7875; l&#7855;ng nghe &yacute; ki&#7871;n ng&#432;&#7901;i kh&aacute;c v&agrave; ch&#7885;n &#273;&uacute;ng th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#432;a ra &yacute; ki&#7871;n c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh l&agrave; c&#7843; m&#7897;t ngh&#7879; thu&#7853;t.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Ch&#7913;ng t&#7887; c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i hay n&#259;ng l&#7921;c c&aacute; nh&acirc;n l&agrave; c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, nh&oacute;m kh&ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i l&agrave; s&acirc;n kh&#7845;u cho ri&ecirc;ng ai. K&#7871;t qu&#7843; cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng m&#7899;i ch&#7913;ng t&#7887; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i trong t&#7853;p th&#7875; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;, trong &#273;&oacute; c&oacute; c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i b&#7843;n th&acirc;n &#273;&atilde; ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh t&#7889;t c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh. M&#7897;t c&aacute; nh&acirc;n s&aacute;ng ch&oacute;i trong khi nh&oacute;m th&#7845;t b&#7841;i th&igrave; c&#361;ng kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; &yacute; ngh&#297;a g&igrave;. &ldquo;Trong m&#7897;t cu&#7897;c &#273;ua ch&#7841;y ti&#7871;p s&#7913;c, hai th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n A, B v&#7899;i ti&#7873;m l&#7921;c c&aacute; nh&acirc;n cao nh&#432;ng l&#7841;i kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; th&#7889;ng nh&#7845;t v&#7899;i nhau ai l&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i ch&#7841;y k&#7871; ti&#7871;p trong l&#432;&#7907;t t&#7899;i. V&#7899;i th&#7901;i gian &#273;&oacute;, c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a &#273;&#7897;i kh&aacute;c tuy ti&#7873;m l&#7921;c c&aacute; nh&acirc;n y&#7871;u h&#417;n ch&uacute;t nh&#432;ng l&#7841;i c&oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p cao n&ecirc;n &#273;&atilde; gi&agrave;nh chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng&rdquo;.</span></p>
<figure id="attachment_10579" style="width: 565px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img class="size-full wp-image-10579" src="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/%C3%BD-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-v%C3%A0-ti%E1%BB%81n-b%E1%BA%A1c.png" alt="(Ngu&#7891;n: Internet)" width="565" height="306" srcset="http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/&yacute;-t&#432;&#7903;ng-v&agrave;-ti&#7873;n-b&#7841;c.png 565w, http://static.techtalk.vn/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/&yacute;-t&#432;&#7903;ng-v&agrave;-ti&#7873;n-b&#7841;c-300x162.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 565px) 100vw, 565px"><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">(Ngu&#7891;n: Internet)</figcaption></figure><p class="p1"><span class="s1">V&#7899;i m&#7897;t v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873;, ch&uacute;ng ta th&#432;&#7901;ng ti&#7871;p c&#7853;n v&#7899;i tri&#7871;t l&yacute; th&#7855;ng-thua cao khi &#273;&ograve;i h&#7887;i quy&#7873;n l&#7907;i b&#7843;n th&acirc;n c&aacute; nh&acirc;n nhi&#7873;u h&#417;n. Th&#432;&#7901;ng l&agrave; sa &#273;&agrave; v&agrave;o c&aacute;c ti&#7875;u ti&#7871;t m&agrave; qu&ecirc;n &#273;i c&aacute;i &#273;&#7841;i c&#7909;c. R&otilde; r&agrave;ng, khi &#273;&oacute; y&#7871;u t&#7889; t&acirc;m l&yacute; &#273;&atilde; l&#7845;n &aacute;t &yacute; ch&iacute;. C&ugrave;ng quan &#273;i&#7875;m, n&#7871;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a ra k&egrave;m theo d&#7919; ki&#7879;n v&agrave; t&#432; duy logic th&igrave; s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7855;ng nghe v&agrave; &#273;&#7891;ng thu&#7853;n h&#417;n l&agrave; khi m&agrave; cu&#7897;c tranh lu&#7853;n sa &#273;&agrave; v&agrave;o c&atilde;i v&#7843; th&#7855;ng thua c&aacute; nh&acirc;n.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">M&#7863;t kh&aacute;c, trong m&#7897;t ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng t&#7853;p th&#7875;, t&acirc;m l&yacute; ng&#7841;i va ch&#7841;m ch&#7911; th&#7875; khi&#7871;n m&#7897;t c&aacute; nh&acirc;n kh&ocirc;ng d&aacute;m &#273;&#432;a ra quan &#273;i&#7875;m c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh, n&#7875; nang ngay c&#7843; khi c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n kh&aacute;c ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng kh&ocirc;ng hi&#7879;u qu&#7843;. B&#7843;n th&acirc;n c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c l&#7907;i v&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;m m&#7871;ch l&ograve;ng ai, nh&#432;ng nh&oacute;m s&#7869; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&#7889;t. D&#7877; d&atilde;i cho qua s&#7869; l&agrave;m hi&#7879;u q&#7911;a c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c t&#7853;p th&#7875; gi&#7843;m &#273;i.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">T&oacute;m l&#7841;i, &#273;i&#7873;u t&ocirc;i mu&#7889;n g&#7917;i t&#7899;i b&#7841;n &#273;&#7885;c b&agrave;i vi&#7871;t n&agrave;y v&agrave; c&#361;ng noted l&#7841;i b&agrave;i h&#7885;c cho ch&iacute;nh t&ocirc;i khi l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c &#273;&oacute; l&agrave; h&atilde;y ch&#7885;n &#273;i&#7875;m r&#417;i th&iacute;ch h&#7907;p cho c&aacute;i t&ocirc;i c&aacute; nh&acirc;n khi l&agrave;m vi&#7879;c nh&oacute;m!</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em>Techtalk via <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/c%C3%A1c-tr%E1%BB%9F-ng%E1%BA%A1i-c%E1%BB%A7a-ng%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Di-vi%E1%BB%87t-nam-khi-l%C3%A0m-vi%E1%BB%87c-nh%C3%B3m-tuan-anh-vu">linkedin</a>&nbsp;</em></span></p></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";s:7:"Hieu Le";s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";N;}s:4:"date";s:19:"2016-11-05 12:00:43";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}}i:8;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:42:"Tản mạn một bài toán trong Project";s:4:"link";s:58:"http://techtalk.vn/tan-man-mot-bai-toan-trong-project.html";s:11:"description";s:617:"<div>C&aacute;ch gi&#7843;i &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n [crayon-582030b9a089f736866253/] Problem: &#272;i&#7873;u g&igrave; s&#7869; s&#7843;y ra l&agrave; thay 1000 b&#7857;ng 10^6 ho&#7863;c m&#7897;t s&#7889; l&#7899;n h&#417;n n&#7919;a? m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh c&oacute; t&iacute;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c lu&ocirc;n (10^6)^(10^6)? k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m tr&ecirc;n google theo c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i, v&agrave; h&#7885; c&#361;ng h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n c&aacute;ch gi&#7843;m s&#7889; ph&eacute;p module l&#7841;i( d&#7921;a v&agrave;o th&#7901;i gian [&hellip;]</div>";s:7:"content";s:8607:"<div><p class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>C&aacute;ch gi&#7843;i &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n</b></span></p>
<p></p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">sum((pow(i,i) for i in range(1,1000))) % 10**10</pre><p></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>Problem</b>: &#272;i&#7873;u g&igrave; s&#7869; s&#7843;y ra l&agrave; thay 1000 b&#7857;ng 10^6 ho&#7863;c m&#7897;t s&#7889; l&#7899;n h&#417;n n&#7919;a? m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh c&oacute; t&iacute;nh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c lu&ocirc;n (10^6)^(10^6)?</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s2"><a href="http://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-48-last-ten-digits/">k&#7871;t qu&#7843; t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m tr&ecirc;n google</a></span><span class="s1"> theo c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m b&ecirc;n d&#432;&#7899;i, v&agrave; h&#7885; c&#361;ng h&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n c&aacute;ch gi&#7843;m s&#7889; ph&eacute;p module l&#7841;i( d&#7921;a v&agrave;o th&#7901;i gian th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n ph&eacute;p so s&aacute;nh nhanh h&#417;n ph&eacute;p module trong m&#7897;t s&#7889; case) s&#7869; l&agrave;m t&#259;ng t&#7889;c &#273;&#7897;</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">L&#7907;i d&#7909;ng 2 t&iacute;nh ch&#7845;t c&#7911;a ph&eacute;p to&aacute;n module d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y</span></p>
<p></p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">(a*b) % c = ((a % c) * (b % c) )% c (1)
(a+b) % c = ((a % c) + (b % c) )% c (2)</pre><p></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>Solution</b></span></p>
<p></p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">modulo = 10**10
    result = 0
    for i in range(1,10**6):
        temp = i
        for j in range(1,i):
            temp *= i
            temp %= modulo

        result += temp
        result %= modulo
    print result</pre><p></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>Discussion</b> C&aacute;ch n&agrave;y s&#7869; cho k&#7871;t qu&#7843; nh&#432;ng ch&#7855;c l&agrave; ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7907;i l&acirc;u. C&oacute; c&aacute;ch n&agrave;o &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;i quy&#7871;t b&agrave;i to&aacute;n n&agrave;y?</span></p>
<ul class="ul1"><li class="li1"><span class="s1">T&igrave;m ra 1 c&ocirc;ng th&#7913;c to&aacute;n h&#7885;c, t&iacute;nh 1 ph&aacute;t ra lu&ocirc;n( M&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng bi&#7871;t, c&oacute; b&#7841;n n&agrave;o bi&#7871;t b&#7843;o m&igrave;nh v&#7899;i nh&eacute;)</span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">T&igrave;m c&aacute;ch c&#7843;i thi&#7879;n vi&#7879;c t&iacute;nh (a^a % modulo)</span></li>
</ul><p class="p2"><span class="s1"><b>Thay &#273;&#7893;i c&aacute;ch t&iacute;nh (a^a % modulo)</b></span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Th&ecirc;m m&#7897;t t&iacute;nh ch&#7845;t c&#7911;a ph&eacute;p l&#361;y th&#7915;a</span></p>
<p></p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">a^(x+y) = a^x * a^y (3)</pre><p></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">&Aacute;p d&#7909;ng (1) v&agrave; (3) ta c&oacute; th&#7875; c&#7843;i ti&#7871;n code theo c&aacute;ch d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y</span></p>
<p></p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">modulo = 10**10

def module_of_sum(a, b, modulo):
    return (a + b) % modulo

def module_of_pow(a, n):
    """
    caculate module pow
    """
    if n == 0:
        return 1
    if n == 1:
        return a % modulo
    tmp = module_of_pow(a, n/2)
    return (tmp*tmp*module_of_pow(a, n - n/2*2)) % modulo

for i in range(1, 10**6):
    total_of_module = module_of_sum(total_of_module, module_of_pow(i, i), modulo)
print "result is {0}".format(total_of_module % modulo)

return total_of_module</pre><p></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>Discussion</b> C&aacute;ch tr&ecirc;n &#273;&atilde; nhanh h&#417;n, v&#7899;i m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh t&#7847;m 14s.</span></p>
<p class="p2"><span class="s1"><b>C&#7843;i ti&#7871;n vi&#7879;c t&iacute;nh (a^a % modulo) m&#7897;t ch&uacute;t</b></span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">N&#7871;u &#273;&#7875; &yacute; m&#7897;t ch&uacute;t b&#7841;n s&#7869; th&#7845;y:</span></p>
<ul class="ul1"><li class="li1"><span class="s1">module_of_pow(2,2) v&agrave; module_of_pow(4,4) c&oacute; li&ecirc;n quan g&igrave; kh&ocirc;ng nh&#7881;? b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; l&agrave;m g&igrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7903; &#273;&acirc;y? N&#7871;u b&#7841;n t&igrave;m ra ch&uacute;ng th&igrave; ch&uacute;c m&#7915;ng b&#7841;n, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &aacute;p d&#7909;ng memorize pattern. Tham kh&#7843;o v&#7873; c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y trong b&agrave;i vi&#7871;t <a href="https://kipalog.com/users/VuNhatMinh/mypage"><span class="s2">Memoization and Decorator</span></a>c&#7911;a anh <a href="https://kipalog.com/users/VuNhatMinh/mypage"><span class="s2">V&#361; Nh&#7853;t Minh</span></a></span></li>
<li class="li1"><span class="s1">N&#7871;u b&#7841;n cho r&#7857;ng n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng li&ecirc;n quan t&#7899;i nhau, th&igrave; c&#361;ng xin ch&uacute;c m&#7915;ng b&#7841;n, v&igrave; n&oacute; gi&uacute;p b&#7841;n ngh&#297; &#273;&#7871;n vi&#7879;c t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n song song. Tham kh&#7843;o <a href="https://kipalog.com/posts/Su-dung-coroutine-trong-python-de-cai-dat-thuat-toan-dieu-phoi-cac-request"><span class="s2">S&#7917; d&#7909;ng coroutine trong python &#273;&#7875; c&agrave;i &#273;&#7863;t thu&#7853;t to&aacute;n &#273;i&#7873;u ph&#7889;i c&aacute;c request</span></a> c&#7911;a anh <a href="https://kipalog.com/users/kiennt/mypage"><span class="s2">kiennt</span></a></span></li>
</ul><p class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>C&aacute;ch &aacute;p d&#7909;ng memorize pattern:</b></span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">V&#7899;i k l&agrave; s&#7889; nguy&ecirc;n t&#7889;, v&agrave; vi&#7879;c &aacute;p d&#7909;ng k =2, k= 3, k= 5&hellip; ho&#7863;c &aacute;p d&#7909;ng t&#7845;t c&#7843; l&agrave; do b&#7841;n.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">M&igrave;nh &#273;&atilde; th&#7917; v&#7899;i range(1, 10^6), tr&ecirc;n spec m&aacute;y c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh th&igrave; k&#7871;t qu&#7843; l&agrave; khi &aacute;p d&#7909;ng k = {2,3,5,7} th&igrave; vi&#7879;c t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n nhanh h&#417;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c 40%</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>Solution</b></span></p>
<p></p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">def module_of_pow_using_memorize(k_prime_list):
    """
    apply memorize pattern to cache previos result
    As you see
    If a == k*b:
        a^a = (k*b)^(k*b)
            = ((k*b)^b)^k
            = (k^b * b^b)^k
    In this case, we only consider k is prime number
    because b always less than or equal to a(b &lt;= a),
    so if we cache caculted of b^b and k^b result,
    and using it to caculate a^a
    """
    # array to store b^b
    memory_b = [1]
    # array to store k^b
    memory_k = []

    for i in range(0, max(k_prime_list) + 1):

        # init data for k^0
        memory_k.append(1)

    def wrapper(a, n):
        if n == 0:
            result = 1
            if n == a:
                memory_b.append(result)
            return result

        if n == 1:
            result = (a % modulo)
            if n == a:
                memory_b.append(result)

            return result

        k = 0

        # cache k^b
        for i in k_prime_list:
            if a %i == 0:
                memory_k[i] = (memory_k[i] * i) % modulo
                k = i

        if k != 0:
            memory_k[k] = (memory_k[k]) % modulo

            # caculate a^a
            b = a/k
            result = ((memory_b[b]*memory_k[k])**k) % modulo

            # cache a^a
            memory_b.append(result)

            return result

        tmp = wrapper(a, n/2)
        result = tmp*tmp*wrapper(a, n - n/2*2) % modulo

        if n == a:
            memory_b.append(result)

        return result
    return wrapper</pre><p></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>C&aacute;ch &aacute;p d&#7909;ng t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n song song( m&igrave;nh ch&#432;a implement b&#7857;ng python)</b></span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">M&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; ch&#7881; m&igrave;nh c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y v&agrave; implement b&#7857;ng C++ v&agrave; nh&#7853;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c k&#7871;t qu&#7843; nhanh h&#417;n 75% so v&#7899;i c&aacute;ch t&iacute;nh tu&#7847;n t&#7921; kh&ocirc;ng &aacute;p d&#7909;ng memorize tr&ecirc;n spec m&aacute;y 4 core c&#7911;a anh &#7845;y) ch&#7855;c c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng l&#7841; g&igrave; v&#7899;i c&aacute;c anh trong nh&oacute;m #hardcode</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em>Techtalk via <a href="https://kipalog.com/posts/Tan-man-mot-bai-toan-trong-ProjectEuler">kipalog</a></em></span></p></div>";s:6:"author";O:16:"SimplePie_Author":3:{s:4:"name";s:7:"Hieu Le";s:4:"link";N;s:5:"email";N;}s:4:"date";s:19:"2016-11-05 07:00:57";s:10:"enclosures";a:1:{i:0;O:19:"SimplePie_Enclosure":27:{s:7:"bitrate";N;s:8:"captions";N;s:10:"categories";N;s:8:"channels";N;s:9:"copyright";N;s:7:"credits";N;s:11:"description";N;s:8:"duration";N;s:10:"expression";N;s:9:"framerate";N;s:7:"handler";N;s:6:"hashes";N;s:6:"height";N;s:10:"javascript";N;s:8:"keywords";N;s:4:"lang";N;s:6:"length";N;s:4:"link";N;s:6:"medium";N;s:6:"player";N;s:7:"ratings";N;s:12:"restrictions";a:1:{i:0;O:21:"SimplePie_Restriction":3:{s:12:"relationship";s:5:"allow";s:4:"type";N;s:5:"value";s:7:"default";}}s:12:"samplingrate";N;s:10:"thumbnails";N;s:5:"title";N;s:4:"type";N;s:5:"width";N;}}}i:9;O:8:"stdClass":7:{s:5:"title";s:77:"21 nguồn mở tuyệt vời để viết các ứng dụng iOS bằng Swift";s:4:"link";s:41:"http://techtalk.vn/21-nguon-mo-swift.html";s:11:"description";s:607:"<div>Series nh&#7919;ng d&#7921; &aacute;n ngu&#7891;n m&#7903; &#7845;n t&#432;&#7907;ng. Swift&nbsp;l&agrave; 1 ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; l&#7853;p tr&igrave;nh m&#7909;c &#273;&iacute;ch chung, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c Apple ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n cho iOS, OS X, watchOS v&agrave; tvOS. Hi&#7879;n t&#7841;i, &#273;&acirc;y l&agrave; ng&ocirc;n ng&#7919; ngu&#7891;n m&#7903; n&#7893;i ti&#7871;ng nh&#7845;t tr&ecirc;n Github. Mybridge AI&nbsp;&#273;&atilde; &#273;&aacute;nh gi&aacute; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng n&#7897;i dung v&agrave; x&#7871;p h&#7841;ng nh&#7919;ng b&agrave;i vi&#7871;t [&hellip;]</div>";s:7:"content";s:18084:"<div><p id="8bcd" class="graf graf--p graf-after--h3">Series nh&#7919;ng d&#7921; &aacute;n ngu&#7891;n m&#7903; &#7845;n t&#432;&#7907;ng.</p>
